 imited time utilizing Bro in a production environment\, so I plan to setup 
 a new sensor and mess around Bro's capabilities.  I hope we can get a plan 
 on some future goals of things we want to explore in Bro as well as some ex
 perienced Bro users to come in and speak on how they utilize Bro in unique 
 ways that may benefit others.  \nhttp://www.meetup.com/Unallocated-Space/ev
 ents/230827285/
