UID:0q0q740p103hcf9r6826lipts0@google.com
CREATED:20171216T230211Z
DESCRIPTION:The UnlloCTF team has grown\, and a new CTF is coming up shortl
 y.  Come show off your attack skills!  Unallocated Space will host an attac
 k-style Capture-The-Flag competition on Memorial Day (Monday\, May 26th\, 2
 014).  No qualifiers are necessary\; it’s first-come-first-serve.\n\nThere 
 are 7 slots for on-site teams and an additional 13 slights for remote (VPN)
  teams\, although on-site teams will have an advantage.  Each team will hav
 e 6 hours (2pm-8pm Eastern) to compromise targets and capture flags.\n\nThe
  cost is $25/team for up to 5 players (If there are concerns/problems with 
 this cost\, scholarships are available.  Send us a email).  Prizes will inc
 lude Trophies\, UAS shirts and CASH.\n\nIf you have any questions\, feel fr
 ee to email us at UnalloCTF {at} unallocatedspace {dot} org.\n\nRules will 
 be provided prior to the event and judges will be on-site.  Obviously\, any
  DoS/MitM attacks\, attempts to impede other teams\, or attacking the envir
 onment may result in loss of points or disqualification.\n\nYou will receiv
 e a email shortly after Registration asking for the emails\, and handles/na
 mes of each member of your team.  We need both for you to be able to partic
 ipate.\n\nRegistration is open at https://unalloctf2014.eventbrite.com
LAST-MODIFIED:20171216T232911Z
LOCATION:Unallocated Space\, Shaw Court\, Severn\, MD\, United States
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:UnalloCTF - POSTPONED
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
