DESCRIPTION:The Minicon is a event dedicated to sharing what we have learne
 d with others. Speakers can use this as a way to practice their talks befor
 e conferences and/or just practice their speaking skills and get feedback. 
 If you have a request for a topic or are interested in giving a talk\, cont
 act Forgotten via the google group\, meetup group\, in person or whatever o
 ther medium you prefer. If any presenters want to share their presentation\
 , please make a request via our Github.\n\nhttps://unallocatedspace.org/eve
 nts/minicon/\n\nOriginally called Textile’s Sewer (since soiree is hard to 
 pronounce and spell)\, this event is dedicated to sharing information about
  anything technical or just awesome. As Technology Enthusiasts\, most of us
  are constantly learning about new technologies.  
LAST-MODIFIED:20171216T232911Z
LOCATION:Unallocated Space\, 512 Shaw Court #105\, Severn\, MD\, United Sta
 tes
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Minicon
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
