 -Mail arduino@unallocatedspace.org.  We have a few of all of the required i
 tems\, but we need to know how many to prepare.\n\nSince the space runs off
  of donations\, we would like to mention that the recommended donation for 
 this class is $5. It is by no means a requirement!  Attendance to the space
