  to come by and chat\, work on a project\, get help with something\, or jus
 t dork around.  I might be working on getting the death bot wired and clean
 ed up as well.  All depends on who shows up :)\n\nJust as a heads up: Durin
 g this informal event\, there will be some folks setting up for the LAN par
 ty that takes place tomorrow.\n\nI'll hang around until either everyone is 
 gone\, or 10 PM rolls around.\n\n-Proto
