DESCRIPTION:The Minicon is a time block dedicated to sharing knowledge\, te
 sting conference presentations and improving presentation skills.  The 4 ho
 ur block is broken up into a 4-8 presentations each lasting up to an hour.\
 n\nForgotten is looking for speakers who want to test conference presentati
 ons\, share some knowledge\, and/or practice their speaking skills.  Length
  is between 15 minutes and 1 hour.  Projector is available\, but you don't 
 need slides if you prefer not to.  I have some suggestions and a historical
  record of talks which may give you some ideas at the following URL:\n\nhtt
 p://www.unallocatedspace.org/uas/minicon\n\nWe need your help to make this 
 event a success.  Regardless of what your experience is in\, there are peop
 le who will almost always find it interesting to learn about.
LAST-MODIFIED:20171216T232911Z
LOCATION:Unallocated Space\, 512 Shaw Court #105\, Severn\, MD\, United Sta
 tes
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Minicon
TRANSP:OPAQUE
