UID:3dhcgvc4lnb94c0kndcqeo9el8@google.com
CREATED:20171216T230211Z
DESCRIPTION:Do you have an interest in Morse Code?   Would you like to see 
 how it's possible to send intelligent radio signals for hundreds of miles w
 ith just milliwatts of power?\n\nCome out for CW/QRP night!\n\nOur first me
 eting will be on Tuesday night 7/5/16 from 7 to 10pm.\n\nThis first meeting
  will be to discuss what people are looking to get out of this and to provi
 de some tips on learning Morse Code\, the fundamental mode of communication
 s for QRP or low power communications.  We'll also give you some tips on ho
 w you can use today's tech to decode this and see what everyone is talking 
 about without even knowing Morse Code!\nEveryone who attends will receive a
  Morse Code cheat sheet with each of the letters and some of the special Q 
 codes commonly used in CW communications.\n\nEven If your not sure if you'd
  be interested in this\, come on out anyway to learn about this popular par
 t of the Amateur Radio hobby.\n\n73's and 88's!
LAST-MODIFIED:20171216T232911Z
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:CW/QRP Night
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
