DESCRIPTION:Topic: digitalWrite\n\nAgenda:\n7:00 to 9:00\nunderstanding I/O
  pins\npinMode\ndigitalWrite\nPin 13 and "hello world" from an Arduino\n\n9
 :00 to 10:00\nextending and expanding on what we learned\nwork or assistanc
 e on any existing projects\nshow and tell\n\nThings to bring:\nArduino Uno 
 compatible board\nA computer with Arduino software installed\nUSB cable to 
 connect Arduino and computer\n\nOptional:\nBreadboard and wires\nMore LEDs 
 or other low power (5 volt\, <200mA) devices you want to try and turn on.\n
 Any projects you are working on and want to show off\, need help with\, or 
 want to work on
