DESCRIPTION:We're hosting a Code & Coffee event with our friends from Girl 
 Develop It - Baltimore Chapter.\n\n---------\n\nCome Join Us for Code and C
 offee! \n\nThis month we'll be having Code and Coffee at Unallocated! We'd 
 like to thank them for providing the space and the coffee and snacks! \n\nC
 ode & Coffee is an opportunity for you to practice your skills\, meet new f
 riends\, get to know teachers\, and get help if you need it. Bring your lap
 top\, your recent projects\, and your programming problems!  Or just come t
 o get to know us and ask any questions you may have about Girl Develop It! 
  \n\nAll are welcome regardless of gender or skill level\, whether or not y
 ou've attended past Girl Develop It events. \n\nCode & Coffee events are re
 laxed and informal\, and are intended as a way for our community to work an
 d play together while providing each other with ongoing support and feedbac
 k. Feel free to come for the full time or drop in whenever you can -- there
 's no agenda. We can't wait to see you!\n\nNOTE: \nAll GDI events require t
 hat all participants abide by our Code of Conduct: \nhttps://www.girldevelo
 pit.com/code-of-conduct
LAST-MODIFIED:20171216T232911Z
LOCATION:Unallocated Space\, 512 Shaw Court #105\, Severn\, MD 21144\, Unit
 ed States
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Code & Coffee w/GirlDevelopIt
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
