 UAS ham night for an interactive course on toroid inductors!  Tom\, K3CXW\,
  will be leading this hands on interactive event.  There\, he will help us 
 to understand:\n\n- what is an inductor?\n- why do we need them?\n- how do 
 we build them?\n\nNow for the important details:\n\nWhen:  Friday March 13 
 2015 at 7pm.\nWhere: at UAS of course!  512 Shaw Ct Severn MD.\n\nCome on o
 ut and let's roll some toroids!\n\n73's
