 f a\npaid network?  Then Ham Radio Night is for you!\n\nAt this meeting we 
 will cover ham shack operations.   Corey and I will be working on getting i
 t setup tomorrow evening.  \n\nWe will discuss station procedures\, do's an
 d don'ts and other things.   We will start out with the generic SSB and CW 
 contacts.   Digital will be covered later.\n\nSo come out and let's see wha
 t kind of contacts we can make!\n\n73's
LAST-MODIFIED:20171216T232911Z
SEQUENCE:1
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Ham Radio Night
TRANSP:OPAQUE
