DESCRIPTION:Got an interest in Electronics?  Radio?  or just being able to 
 make\ncontact with someone on the other side of the earth without the use o
 f a\npaid network?  Then Ham Radio Night is for you!\n\nHams do a lot with 
 microcontrollers and electronics.  A good understanding of numbering system
 s can go a long way.  This month I will present a quick and simple way to c
 onvert between 4 different numbering systems.  Bring your pencil and paper 
 as we will be going old school to show you how we can show the same number 
 4 different ways!\n\nWe will also talk about winter projects coming up and 
 start our planning for 2016!\n\nHope to see you there!\n\n73's
LAST-MODIFIED:20171216T232911Z
SEQUENCE:1
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Ham Radio Night
TRANSP:OPAQUE
