DESCRIPTION:Greetings!\n\nThis Friday is Ham Radio Night.\n\nThis month we 
 will start planning Field day operations.  We will list our goals that we w
 ant to accomplish for this year.   Since we are looking at a different loca
 tion this year\, we will need different items. Such as needed shelters\, fo
 od\, and other logistics.\n\nSince we will be in a more public location\, w
 e will really need an information table so I'm hoping we can get more volun
 teers from the general membership to come and hang out with us.\n\nSo come 
 on out and find out what it's all about.\n\nGot an interest in Electronics?
   Radio?  or just being able to make\ncontact with someone on the other sid
 e of the earth without the use of a\npaid network?  Then Ham Radio Night is
  for you!\n\nOur topic for this event will be Show and Tell.   Bring your l
 atest\nproject and compare notes with others.  The project can be completed
 \, in\nprocess\, or just planned.  Bring it and let's discuss it!\n\nOther 
 topics of business to be discussed will include:\nUpdate on the Tower Trail
 er Project.\nFuture Fox Hunts.\nUpcoming contests.\n\n73's
LAST-MODIFIED:20171216T232911Z
LOCATION:512 Shaw Court #105\, Severn\, MD\, United States
SEQUENCE:1
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Ham Radio Night
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
