DESCRIPTION:CQ CQ CQ de W3UAS\n\nSorry for the delay in getting this out..\
 n\nTomorrow's Ham night we will take the next step in preparing for field d
 ay.   \n\nEveryone is encouraged to bring any Ham related pictures/ stories
  /information with them as we will be updating the W3UAS QRZ page.  \n\nWe 
 will congratulate the new Techs that passed their exams at the Odenton hamf
 est last week.   Our group is growing and that's a great thing!\n\nI am exp
 ecting a visit by the ARRL MDC section manager\, Marty Pittinger.  We met h
 im at the hamfest and he was so interested\, we invited him out to visit us
  and see how we can promote Ham Radio in the area.\n\nSo come one\, and com
 e all!\n\n73's
LAST-MODIFIED:20171216T232911Z
SEQUENCE:1
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Ham Radio Night
TRANSP:OPAQUE
