DESCRIPTION:Attention all Hams!  And others interested in promoting the spa
 ce!\n\nThis Friday is Ham Night at UAS!   7-10 pm.\n\nThis month\, we will 
 continue planning field day\, but this meeting is one to not miss!  We will
  be discussing Greenbelt Park and at which site would we like to operate fr
 om.  Then we will discuss the operating plans we will need to spell out for
  the park.  \n\nWe will update our needs list with items we will need and w
 ho will volunteer to bring them.  Also\, we may do some tower maintenance a
 s it appears our antenna may have moved in the heavy wind recently.\n\nWe w
 ill need an information table at the event and we will need people willing 
 to come out and talk about the space to the public.\n\nSo come on out for t
 his big planning event!\n\n73's\n\nCharlie. KB3ZVN
LAST-MODIFIED:20171216T232911Z
SEQUENCE:1
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Ham Radio Night
TRANSP:OPAQUE
