DESCRIPTION:Field day is almost upon us!   This Friday we will be putting t
 he finishing touches on our Field day Planning.  All who are hoping to atte
 nd field day should come out to this planning meeting.\n\nWe should also no
 te that this SATURDAY 6/11/16 from 10am to ???  we will be testing our gear
  and doing a preliminary pack up in preparation for Field day.\n\nField day
  is the weekend of Saturday 6/25 through Sunday 6/26 2pm to 2pm. at Greenbe
 lt Park.   it's a 24 hour event and we will need volunteers to come out and
  hang with us.  You don't have to work a radio if you don't want to but we 
 encourage everyone to give it a try!\n\nWe will also have our display table
 s on show for everyone to see.  This will be a great way to get the word ou
 t about UAS and boost membership!  \n\nSo Put Field day weekend on your cal
 endar and plan on attending Ham Radio night this Friday at 7pm!\n\n73's
LAST-MODIFIED:20171216T232911Z
SEQUENCE:1
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Ham Radio Night
TRANSP:OPAQUE
