DESCRIPTION:We will pick up from last time with R2R ladders and operational
  amplifiers. If you have an oscilloscope\, please bring it! By then end of 
 the night we should be playing music through our Arduinos.\n\nAgenda\n1. Op
 erational Amplifiers (voltage feedback only)\n2. Digital to Analog Conversi
 on (R2R Ladder)\n3. Sampling Audio With Arduino\n\nRequired Items\n1. Lapto
 p (Needs to have an audio jack)\n2. Arduino (Any kind will do)\n3. Breadboa
 rd\n4. Jumper wires\n5. USB cable for your Arduino\n\nProvided Items\n1. Op
 erational Amplifier\n2. Audio cable\n3. Resistors (2K ohm)\n4. Small speake
 rs\n\nIf you need any items in the required items section\, please E-Mail u
 as.arduino@gmail.com. We have a few of all of the required items\, but we n
 eed to know how many to prepare.\n\n\n\nSince the space runs off of donatio
 ns\, we would like to mention that the recommended donation for this class 
 is $10. It is by no means a requirement! Attendance to the space\, and this
  class\, is 100% free to all!
LAST-MODIFIED:20171216T232911Z
LOCATION:Unallocated Space
SEQUENCE:1
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Arduino Night
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
