DESCRIPTION:Thanks to the efforts of a great many members of the UAS commun
 ity\, all of the generous donations we've received have been organized.  We
 've realized that we just can not use a lot of this hardware right now.  As
  a result\, we'd like to sell this hardware as part of a fundraising effort
 .  Obviously\, we'll be keeping some of the goodies for the space\, but we'
 d like to spread the love.\n\nBefore anything happens\, we want to make sur
 e you have a chance to voice your concerns.  A lot of you have donated hard
 ware that has helped us significantly.  Some of you have brought in hardwar
 e as a project.  If you see any hardware that is part of your project or so
 mething truly special\, please let us know by Friday night.  We want to mak
 e sure that hardware is kept safe and sound.  Check out the photos on our G
 allery and reply here if there are items that need to be kept:\n\n    http:
 //www.unallocatedspace.org/gallery/main.php?g2_itemId=14\n\nAs part of this
  effort\, we'll be holding a Flea Market next Saturday from 1000-1400.  Cur
 rent keyholders will be allowed in an hour early (that's 0900) for a sneak 
 peek.  Please stop in\, browse around\, and make an offer.  100% of our sal
 es will go directly to the space.  At a minimum\, there are plenty of uniqu
 e pieces of hardware to make it an interesting day!\n\n\nThanks\,\n-- Suref
 ire\n
LAST-MODIFIED:20171216T232911Z
LOCATION:Unallocated Space
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:UAS FleaMarket
TRANSP:OPAQUE
