DESCRIPTION:(This pairs with last night's directional-antenna build night!)
 \n\nCorey will be organizing a foxhunt!  (That's ham radio parlance for usi
 ng direction-finding to locate a radio that's hidden somewhere nearby.)  Yo
 u don't need a ham radio license to participate -- just join a team!\n\nMee
 t at the space at 0900 for the kickoff and rules.  We'll organize an after-
 action meeting at Friscoe Grille (in Columbia) around 1500.\n\nWatch the ma
 iling list for details.
