CREATED:20171216T230211Z
DESCRIPTION:For this LAN Party\, we will be running our first ever *Table F
 lipping* event. We decided to try this awesome idea out after seeing how mu
 ch fun it was at MAGFest.\n\nWe’ll be running this event to raise funds for
  the space. We have determined the following ‘tables’ for your flipping and
  destructive pleasure. >:D\n\n– A bare table can be flipped.\n– A “Kitchen 
 Table” can be flipped\, with tablecloth and (fake) food/items.\n– A “Toys T
 able” can be flipped\, with stuffed animals / toys.\n– A “Gaming Table” can
  be flipped\, with board games and cards.\n– A “Office Supplies” table can 
 be flipped\, with stapler/tape/keyboard/etc\,\n– A “Printing Station Table”
  can be flipped\, with a printer/scanner/etc. and office supplies.\n– A “Te
 ch Table” can be flipped\, with a Laptop and other office/tech items.\n– UP
 GRADE: We’ll make the “Tech Table” a workstation/tower instead of a laptop.
 \n– ADD-ON: You can also add-on use of a baseball bat to follow up your fli
 p and smash the laptop/tower/printer for 10 seconds of pure destructive bli
 ss. “PC LOAD LETTER?!!” …Want more time? Stack this add-on!\n\nDonation lev
 els for each table are currently TBA\, but will start at $20. We will accep
 t cash and paypal donations for this event.\n\nWe will provide safety glass
 es or you can bring your own. Supplies for this event are limited. So\, sho
 w up and sign up early!!\n\nWe’ll run this for at least 5 hours\, during wh
 ich\, we’ll also be grilling food and gaming. So\, come hang out and behold
  the mayhem.\n\nSchedule:\nNoon-3pm: LAN Party Setup / Pick-up Games / Tabl
 e Flipping Event\n3pm-5pm: Grilling Food / More Table Flipping / Tourney / 
 More Gaming\n5pm-12am: All the fragging fun you can handle…\n\nFood will be
  provided\, but feel free to bring additional food to share or a cash donat
 ion for the space. 
LAST-MODIFIED:20171216T232911Z
LOCATION:Unallocated Space\, 512 Shaw Ct #105\, Severn\, MD 21144\, United 
 States
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Epic LAN Party AND Table Flip Event!!
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
