UID:6llffj5s8koq4ete5rdjqenl2g@google.com
CREATED:20171216T230211Z
DESCRIPTION:5:00 – Doors open\n6:00 – Gaming starts\n7:30 – Pizza arrives (
 $5/person)\n9:00 – Tournament begins\n??:?? – Everyone goes home happy (som
 etime after midnight)\n\nWe’ll enjoy pizza\, drinks\, and gaming the night 
 away. We’ll have servers running for our old favorites (UT2k4\, TF2\, L4D2)
 \, but we’re looking to mix it up a bit. We’ve got our own ideas\, but we r
 eally want YOUR ideas\, so please take a minute to fill out a really quick 
 survey.\n\nPLEASE RSVP via the survey (or just reply to this thread\, if yo
 u’d rather) so we save a seat for you.\n\nHope to see you there!\n– Surefir
 e\, Nonie\, and Wrecker\n
LAST-MODIFIED:20171216T232911Z
LOCATION:Unallocated Space\, 512 Shaw Ct\, #105\, Severn\, MD\, 21144
SEQUENCE:1
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:LAN Party
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
