DESCRIPTION:DATE: 17AUG2017\nTIME: 1930-2130\nTOPIC: INFOSEC NIGHT: Browser
  Extensions\nSUMMARY: I’m keeping it easy tonight. I want to have an open d
 iscussion on browser\nextensions. Not all the extensions I use are security
  related some are for work flow and for fun.\nSome are informational and I’
 m sure there are many more I could be using and I am not. There\nare thousa
 nds and thousands of extensions to use and some are amazingly helpful. I ju
 st want\nto bring people together and share because trying to read through 
 reviews is cringe worthy.\nAnd it’s always great to get first hand knowledg
 e. I will also briefly go over and cover security\nproblems with extensions
  as well.\nGOAL: To share and improve each others browser experience with a
  touch of security\nThings to bring: Your laptop and maybe a few different 
 browsers installed. Not all extensions\nare available on a particular brows
 er.\nHomework:\nNone\nSKILL LEVEL: Everyone\nPRESENTER: Wasabi
LAST-MODIFIED:20171216T232911Z
LOCATION:Unallocated Space\, 512 Shaw Ct #105\, Severn\, MD 21144\, USA
SEQUENCE:1
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:INFOSEC Night: Browser Extensions
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
