DESCRIPTION:DATE: 24AUG2017\nTIME: 1930-2130\nTOPIC: INFOSEC NIGHT: Your Re
 sume Sucks Let’s FIX it!!\nSUMMARY: We all have read Job postings and thoug
 ht WTF. We all have submitted a\nResume and never heard anything back. We a
 ll have thought we figured out the system. Or\nmaybe you are changing jobs 
 and have not needed to write a resume before and need one\nnow.\nMark Horni
 ng a Technical/INFOSEC Recruiter from Tresys in Columbia MD will be here to
  help.\nHe will not be there to recruit you for his company. He is going to
  tell you why you are probably\nnot getting that job you want at another co
 mpany. He will tell you about all the resumes he has\nto sort through and w
 hat made him cringe. He will Tell you why he does not pick certain\nresumes
  or what he wishes you would explain something better to find a good fit fo
 r you. He will\ntry to explain why things are written the way they are on j
 ob postings or what they mean.\nGOAL: To have a better understanding about 
 resumes\, job postings\, and hiring in the\nINFOSEC/Tech Industry.\n\nHomew
 ork:\nFind a few job requirements or job descriptions for your field or sli
 ce of INFOSEC. And bring\nyour resume just in case to update or get it revi
 ewed if there is time.\nSKILL LEVEL: Everyone\nPRESENTER: Mark Horning.
LAST-MODIFIED:20171216T232911Z
LOCATION:Unallocated Space\, 512 Shaw Ct #105\, Severn\, MD 21144\, USA
SEQUENCE:1
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:INFOSEC NIGHT: Your Resume Sucks Let’s FIX it!!
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
