DESCRIPTION:UPDATED: 06-SEP 17:16 EDT\n\nThis morning\, several members bro
 ught to our attention concerns over the privacy implications of using donat
 ed hardware for our forensics class.  On such short notice\, we have been u
 nable to reconcile these ethical and legal concerns.  It is not our policy 
 to perform forensics on donated hardware unless said hardware was specifica
 lly donated for that purpose.  As a result\, we have decided to cancel this
  Thursday’s Forensics class.  We hope to have a sanitized image for a later
  offering.
LAST-MODIFIED:20171216T232911Z
LOCATION:Unallocated Space\, 512 Shaw Ct #105\, Severn\, MD 21144\, USA
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:CANCELLED -- INFOSEC Night: Random Digital Forensics
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
