 B cable\n3. PySerial installed if you want to use Python to talk to the Ard
 uino\n\nIf you need any items in the required items section\, please E-Mail
  uas.arduino@gmail.com. We have a few of all of the required items\, but we
  need to know how many to prepare.\nSince the space runs off of donations\,
  we would like to mention that the recommended donation for this class is $
 5. It is by no means a requirement! Attendance to the space\, and this clas
 s\, is 100% free to all!
