UID:877tvs0dga078pocps1vncuqc0@google.com
CREATED:20171216T230211Z
DESCRIPTION:Halloween & Horror Epic LAN Party\, October 29th!! 12 HOURS of 
 Haunting Good Fun from noon til midnight!!\n\nWe knew you were dying to com
 e play some horror-themed games with us on Halloween weekend\, and we didn'
 t want to disappoint!\n\nSaturday\, October 29\, from noon until midnight w
 e will be running another epic 12-hour LAN party -- this time horror-themed
 !\n\nWe've got some other fun things in mind too! We'll have a costume cont
 est for those so inclined to dress up\, a hot seat tournament\, and another
  (TBA) competition which we'll just say will involve pumpkins and be a mess
 y good time.... \;-D\n\nGames you should bring (and update beforehand):\n\n
 L4D2\, Dead Realm\, Necropolis\, Minecraft\, Killing Floor\, Evolve Stage 2
  (F2P)\, Dead by Daylight\n\nIf you have some other favorite horror games y
 ou'd like to suggest\, please do!\n\nFor food\, we'll be grilling again\, b
 ut we also encourage you to bring your favorite themed (or non-themed) dish
  to share. Chips are also perfectly acceptable. \;-)\n\nWe'll be jammin som
 e awesome on-theme beats for the event. So\, come out and get spooky with u
 s! \;-D\n\nAs always\, this event is free\, but running the space is not. S
 o\, we do ask that you make a donation so that we can continue to provide y
 ou with epic fun events like this!\n
LAST-MODIFIED:20171216T232911Z
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Halloween & Horror: Epic LAN Party
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
