DESCRIPTION:Data privacy is more important than ever. Join us at for a sess
 ion devoted to the nuances of cryptography and why it is important than eve
 r to use it. Some of the areas to be covered include: \n \n1- A brief histo
 ry of crypto \n2- The hows and whys of drive encryption \n3- PKI\, PGP\, an
 d digital signatures \n4- How does it all work? \n5- Where do we go from he
 re? \n
LAST-MODIFIED:20171216T232911Z
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Cryptography Workshop
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
