DESCRIPTION:Robot Fest is a annual event for anyone interested in the creat
 ive realm of technology. We welcome all ages of hackers\, hobbyists and mak
 ers with the unquenchable urge to witness and create new\, previously unsee
 n forms from lifeless electronics and mechanical parts. There will be fun a
 nd excitement for all ages at this day long event. \n \nIf you are inexplic
 ably drawn to sites like makezine.com\, hackaday.com\, servomagazine.com\, 
 nutsvolts.com\, or botmag.com\, you will enjoy this day of playful inventio
 n! \n \nNational Electronics Museum\, 1745 West Nursery Road\, Linthicum\, 
 MD 21090 \n \nFor more information: http://www.robotfest.com/ \n \nRobot Fe
 st is a annual event for anyone interested in the creative realm of technol
 ogy. We welcome all ages of hackers\, hobbyists and makers with the unquenc
 hable urge to witness and create new\, previously unseen forms from lifeles
 s electronics and mechanical parts. There will be fun and excitement for al
 l ages at this day long event. \n \nIf you are inexplicably drawn to sites 
 like makezine.com\, hackaday.com\, servomagazine.com\, nutsvolts.com\, or b
 otmag.com\, you will enjoy this day of playful invention! \n \nNational Ele
 ctronics Museum \n1745 West Nursery Road \nLinthicum\, MD 21090 \n
LAST-MODIFIED:20171216T232911Z
LOCATION:National Electronics Museum in Linthicum
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Robot Fest / Maker Faire
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
