UID:-WWW-UNALLOCATEDSPACE-ORG-CALENDAR-__PUBLIC__-0000000045
CLASS:PUBLIC
CREATED:20171216T230211Z
DESCRIPTION:TexasDex will be giving an introduction to SweetHome3D.   \n \n
 SweetHome 3D is a home layout software package with the nifty ability to vi
 ew the designs in 3 dimensions and generate videos.  It’s not the only piec
 e of software that can do that but it’s free\, open source\, and cross plat
 form.  I’ll be showing you how to use it to plan out your hackerspace\, man
 -cave\, or even plain old home remodeling.  SweetHome3D is easy to install 
 and get started on.  Come watch as I explain how I used it to build the mod
 el of the space above\, and you can even bring your laptop and follow along
  with me! \n \nhttp://www.unallocatedspace.org/uas/2011/05/11/home-design-f
 or-hackers/
LAST-MODIFIED:20171216T232911Z
LOCATION:Unallocated Space
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Home Design for Hackers
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
