UID:-WWW-UNALLOCATEDSPACE-ORG-CALENDAR-__PUBLIC__-0000000053
CLASS:PUBLIC
CREATED:20171216T230211Z
DESCRIPTION:A primer class to understanding wireless networks and hacking i
 nto them. \n \nYou should attend if you want to learn about... \n802.11 Man
 agement frames \nAircrack-ng Project \nMonitor Mode/Injection \nKismet \nAi
 rodump \n \nWe may also do a war drive if there is interest  \n \nI have so
 me wireless cards but people should bring their own cards that are supporte
 d under linux. Please make an effort to determine if it is monitor mode and
  injection capable. I will have BT4 or Pentoo cds for those who do not have
  linux installed on their boxes. -Textile
LAST-MODIFIED:20171216T232911Z
LOCATION:UAS
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:802.11 Hacking Basics
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
