UID:-WWW-UNALLOCATEDSPACE-ORG-CALENDAR-__PUBLIC__-0000000072
CLASS:PUBLIC
CREATED:20171216T230211Z
DESCRIPTION:http://www.nem-electronicafest.com/ \n \nNational Electronics M
 useum \n1745 West Nursery Rd. \nLinthicum\, MD 21090 \n \n \nJoin the Natio
 nal Electronics Museum as we host Electronic Fest 2011 - a day of knob twis
 ting\, pitch bending\, wiring mazes\, sound shaping & visual explosions. On
  the main stage witness an absolutely awesome musical voyage into another g
 alaxy of sound alterations as we present eleven of the area's most exciting
  and innovated musical groups\, featuring national recording and visual art
 ist Arthur Loves Plastic. Meantime in our workshop area build a light contr
 olled synthesizer you can take home and learn how to turn Apps into music. 
 Talk to vendors and tinkers\, witness musical monsters\, and experience the
  latest in effects and enhancements to turn technology into your own musica
 l adventure.  \n \n \nDonation: $8.00 per person ages 15+ \n$4.00 per perso
 n for ages 6 to 14 \nFree entry for ages 5 & below
LAST-MODIFIED:20171216T232911Z
LOCATION:National Electronics museum 
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Electronica Fest 2011
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
