 \, and talking about the Technician exam.  We'll also be picking out hardwa
 re we're going to need to get our Drake TR-7 on the air.\n\nFor those of yo
 u with 2 meter handhelds or mobiles\, the club station (W3UAS) will be moni
 toring 145.550 simplex\, if you'd like to tune in to a talk-in frequency.\n
 \nAround 7:00\, we'll grab some pizza -- so don't let a lack of dinner slow
  you down.  Be careful in the snow\, but we'll have a warm hackerspace and 
 plenty of soda waiting for you when you make it.
