 s they volunteer.  Some talks\, but not all will be recorded \n \n"Monkeyin
 g Around with Tamarin" by Dion \n"Grepping the Gropers : Airport Security" 
 by Cryptos \n"Networks\, What not to do!" by Hunter \n"Your malware has no 
 clothes - moments of cluelessness in the design of modern malicious softwar
 e" by Munin\n“Web App Security Basics” by Chuck\n“Standard Development Envi
 ronments and the theory of Configuration Management” by R00ster
