DESCRIPTION:Georgia Weidman’s Advanced Metasploit Class will review the bas
 ics then move on to advanced topics.   \n \nThere will be a lunch break. \n
  \nYou must register to attend as their will be limited space (http://www.e
 ventbrite.com/event/3706488206).  There will be a cost of $20 cash directly
  to Georgia on the day of the class.  If you have a problem with the cost\,
  please contact Forgotten (Forgotten@forgottensec.com).   \n \nIf you are o
 ne of the lucky few to get registered\, show up 15 minutes early.  If you e
 nd up on the wait list\, I would still show up\, you may or may not get in.
   15 minutes before the start of the event\, I will start to fill the empty
  seats with people from the Wait list in the order of registration.   \n \n
 If you do not register\, you will not be able to join in (keyholders includ
 ed).  There will be no preferential treatment besides the registration orde
 r.   \n \nIf you have any questions\, contact Forgotten (Forgotten@forgotte
 nsec.com)
LAST-MODIFIED:20171216T232911Z
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Advanced Metasploit
TRANSP:OPAQUE
