 seeking 2-3 setup volenteers. \n\nOdenton Fire Hall\n\nTalk in is on the 14
 6.805- repeater with tone 107.2.\n\nFood and drink will be available to pur
 chase. Amateur radio license exams are available at the hamfest. Preregistr
 ation is requested\, but walk-ins are welcome. \n\nWebsite: https://sites.g
 oogle.com/site/marylandmobileers/hamfests-1/hamfest-2\n\nSponsor: Maryland 
 Mobileers Amateur Radio Club\nType: ARRL Hamfest\nTalk-In: 146.805/146.205 
 (PL 107.2)\n\nV\\r\,\nBuddy
