DESCRIPTION:All\,\n\nMovie Night!\n\nTitle: Clue (1985)\nInfo: http://m.imd
 b.com/title/tt0088930/\n\nThere's a tone of movies that we are dying to sha
 re with you. Everything from\n\n    Big Trouble in Little China (1986)\n   
  The Fifth Element (1997)\n    Labyrinth (1986)\n    Gremlins (1984)\n    *
 batteries not included (1987)\n    Ghostbusters (1984)\n    FernGully: The 
 Last Rainforest (1992)\n    Uncle Buck (1989)\n    The Wizard (1989)\n    T
 eenage Mutant Ninja Turtles II: The Secret of the Ooze (1991) \n\nto cult c
 lassics\n\n    Monty Python and the Holy Grail (1975)\n    History of the W
 orld: Part I (1981)\n    The Rocky Horror Picture Show (1975)\n\nPlease joi
 n us for popcorn and a movie at 10pm. See you there!\n\nv/r\nBuddy\n\nP.S. 
 Please share with us what's a "must see movie" on http://unallocatedspace.s
 lack.com.
