CREATED:20171216T230211Z
DESCRIPTION:Topic: Stepper Motors\n\nAgenda:\n7:00pm to 9:00pm\n-Theory of 
 operation\n-manually stepping the motor\n-Stepper.h\n\nWe will be working w
 ith the 28BYJ-48 motor and driver board. So that means motors and blinkenli
 ghts at no extra cost!\n\n9:00pm to 10:00pm\n-extension\n-any other project
 s people are working / need help on\n\nWhat you need to bring:\n-A computer
