DESCRIPTION:If you want to learn how to solder or maybe just brush up on yo
 ur soldering skills\, come by UAS for our soldering class. We will be putti
 ng together the WeevilEye kits donated to UAS by Sparkfun! These kits are s
 uitable for all ages and skill levels.\nWe will have some tools available\,
  but feel free to bring your own soldering iron and flush cutters if you ar
 e more comfortable with your own equipment.\n\nIf you are proficient at sol
 dering and are comfortable teaching\, we're looking for some additional ins
 tructors. Ideally a 1 teacher to 4 student ratio would be best.\n\nSince Un
 allocated Space runs off of donations\, we would like to mention that the r
 ecommended donation for this class is $5. It is by no means a requirement! 
 Attendance to the space\, and this class\, is 100% free to all!
