UID:cb9eq1a9h7961cibnu77pd7ojo@google.com
CREATED:20171216T230211Z
DESCRIPTION:Serial communication with a computer.\n\nEver wanted to send th
 e interesting data your Arduino is collecting back to a PC to do long term 
 storage and analysis?\n\nEver wanted to control your project without pushin
 g buttons on a shield?\n\nEver wanted to talk to your Arduino? Ever wanted 
 it to talk back?\n\n:Basic Topics:\nBytes vs Strings\nSending multiple valu
 es to the PC\nReceiving multiple values from the PC\nActuating a pin remote
 ly\n\n:Advanced Topics:\nSending and receiving multiple values\nDeveloping 
 a simple communication protocol\n\nFor this class we will be using Processi
 ng on the PC. Please goto https://processing.org/download/ and download you
 r OS specific 32bit version. Don't worry all Processing code will be provid
 ed.
LAST-MODIFIED:20171216T232911Z
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Arduino Night
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
