CREATED:20171216T230211Z
DESCRIPTION:Make a project that somehow copies or funnels reassembled\, nor
 malized\, decoded traffic from snort to either a POF preprocessor built int
 o snort\, or into an a stand-alone POF system for analysis. This informatio
 n can be used to build accurate results for asset management\, service dete
 ction\, operating system detection\, etc. and also take advantage of the PO
 F information/database and be used to make suggestions for preprocessor set
 tings (e.g. packet defragmentation and/or stream reassembly configurations)
  and eventually rule recommendations based on services and operating system
 s observed.
