DESCRIPTION:If you’re just now entering the field this will be valuable kno
 wledge to use when entering the IT field. I will also cover things that mos
 t books will not teach you. This should be considered an essential knowledg
 e transfer class. If people like it or enough show up I may consider puttin
 g on more of them.\n \nTopics Covered:\n·         How to DCPromo a machine\
 no   Best practices for naming conventions\n·         DNS and how it is uti
 lized within Active Directory\n·         Overview of Active Directory Users
  and Computers\n·         Overview of Group Policy\n·         Mitigating Pa
 ss the Hash/Ticket attacks\n·         Mitigating Authentication DoS attacks
 \n·         Very basic LDAP queries
