DESCRIPTION:As Technology Enthusiasts\, most of us are constantly learning 
 about new technologies.  The Minicon is a event dedicated to sharing what w
 e have learned with others.  Given that this is not far before ShmooCon\, I
  hope we have some folks practicing their presentations for Shmoo\; I know 
 I will be.  \n\nSpeakers:\n\nThrown Weapons Demo\nA OSX Security Primer\nAn
  introductory explanation of sockets using basic Python\nDemo of GWT/GXT fo
 r web apps – libraries\nForensics Primer\nExploiting Music Streaming with J
 avaScript\nSSH for Pentesters\n“Demystifying InfoSec Challenges” (if there’
 s time)\n\nSuggested Donation: $10\n\nCome learn about what others are work
 ing on and share what your working on.  This also provides a group opportun
 ity to get feedback on a presentation and/or presenting skills (ask specifi
 cally if this is something you want).  \n\nI hope to see you there!
