UID:elpgbjm59or9leupcri4doq10c@google.com
CREATED:20171216T230211Z
DESCRIPTION:DIGITAL INTIMACY explores surveillance psychology of intimate p
 ersonal data as marketplace currency. A multichannel installation merges re
 altime information from sensors surrounding viewers. Information gathered i
 s video-mapped on 1950’s-style kitchen and living room furnishings. Audio c
 hannels include realtime spatialized musical sonifications of live stock ti
 ckers and computer-generated voices narrating text in personal social media
  accounts.\n \nThe following are the general categories of data gathering t
 echnologies we are looking at\, and we’ve been interested in and we want to
  hear the thoughts of security-experienced people.\n \n•Bluetooth\n•RFID\n•
 NFC\n•Optical Character Recognition\n \nSee Project Trailer:\nhttp://cindyk
 onits.com
LAST-MODIFIED:20171216T232911Z
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Intro to Digital Intimacy: a Privacy Project
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
