UID:ficr4or1egt97kbumt2l0sjeh4@google.com
CREATED:20171216T230211Z
DESCRIPTION:WebWithWine Night with GirlDevelopIt-Baltimore @ UnallocatedSpa
 ce\n\nOur regularly scheduled Web Development Night is trying something new
  and bringing you instead\, an evening of WebWithWine (WWW). Come and join 
 us and our friends from Girl Develop It: Baltimore for a night of working o
 n your web related projects\, whether it be web design\, web development\, 
 or web app security. We'll be opening a few bottles or wine\, working on we
 b projects and just generally hanging out.\n\nWWW night is an opportunity f
 or you to practice your skills\, meet new friends\, and get help if you nee
 d it. Bring your laptop\, your recent projects\, and your programming probl
 ems!  Or just come to get to know us and ask any questions you may have abo
 ut Unallocated Space or Girl Develop It!\n\nAll are welcome regardless of g
 ender or skill level. However\, you must be 21 or older to drink. \n\nWWW e
 vents are relaxed and informal\, and are intended as a way for our communit
 y to work and play together while providing each other with ongoing support
  and feedback. Feel free to come for the full time or drop in whenever you 
 can - there's no agenda. We can't wait to see you! \n\nThis event is FREE\,
  but as Unallocated Space runs off of donations\, we would like to mention 
 that a donation of $5 is recommended for most events\, and helps us keep th
 e lights on. However\, there is no charge to attend a WebWithWine event.
LAST-MODIFIED:20171216T232911Z
LOCATION:Unallocated Space\, 512 Shaw Ct #105\, Severn\, MD\, United States
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:WebWithWine Night
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
