UID:fkk16oscddudttlp41huvth860@google.com
CREATED:20171216T230211Z
DESCRIPTION:UnalloCTF Solution Sharing - On Memorial Day\, Surefire and For
 gotten hosted UnalloCTF\, a Pen Testing Style competition focusing on each 
 team's ability to think outside the box and crack into the target network w
 e designed.  Our goal was to make every box exploitable without Metasploit 
 (although there were a few boxes that MSF is the fastest way to).  We had a
  total of 4800 possible points and 13 teams of up to 5 people that competed
  over 6 hours.  We had a awesome prize pool and a amazing sponsor (Art of E
 xploitation).  One of the most important things we wanted to do with Unallo
 CTF was explain how all the captured flags were actually captured.  We hope
  you will come by and listen in as we explain how to compromise the entire 
 first UnalloCTF Network.
LAST-MODIFIED:20171216T232911Z
LOCATION:Unallocated Space\, 512 Shaw Ct\, #105\, Severn\, MD\, 21144
SEQUENCE:2
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:UnalloCTF Solution Sharing
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
