DESCRIPTION:Hangout is live:  https://plus.google.com/hangouts/_/calendar/d
 WFzZm9yZ290dGVuQGdtYWlsLmNvbQ.ge7b8cp7se14puu4g03umso1i0\n\nMonths ago\, we
  set out to make a CTF that we could be proud of.  Unfortunately\, we're ju
 st not there yet.  Rather than give you a sub-par experience\, we'd rather 
 postpone until we can make it the right way.\n\nIn the meantime\, we unders
 tand that you have already reserved your Memorial Day holiday.  In an effor
 t to make it up to you\, we've lined up some CTF-related talks and hands-on
  labs.  Bring your laptop with Kali Linux (version 1.0.6) if you'd like to 
 participate in the hands-on portions of the talks.  Here's what we've got l
 ined up so far:\n\n  - An Introduction to Metasploit and Meterpreter\n  - W
 riting Metasploit Modules\n  - Windows Registry Forensics\n  - Windows OS V
 ulnerabilities\n  - Web Vulns: What they are and how to abuse them\n\nWe'll
  have enough pizza and sodas for everyone.  For our remote teams\, we'll st
 ream the talks for you.  Again\, we're sorry for the inconvenience and hope
  you'll respect our decision.
