UID:hr7ucjo2kikrfm3aejcpdjpkqo@google.com
CREATED:20171216T230211Z
DESCRIPTION:Unallocated Space (UAS) Community Tech Swap Meet/Garage Sale (A
 nne Arundel\, MD)\n\nUnallocated Space\, a 501(c)(3) Hackerspace/Makerspace
  in Severn\, MD Anne Arundel County would like to invite you\, your family\
 , and friends to its second community tech swap meet / garage sale on Satur
 day June 18th 2016 at eight to four\, rain or shine.\n\nThe purpose of the 
 sale is to clear space\, raise money for future projects\, and encourage th
 e community to recycle.\n\nOur mission is to Teach\, Learn\, and Build! See
  the UAS’ blog post for more details\, including directions atwww.unallocat
 edspace.org andhttp://meetu.ps/e/BDJ9v/bkJ5K/d to RSVP.\n\nWHAT WILL YOU FI
 ND?\n\nAnything is possible. Things to expect to see for sale will vary\, b
 ut here are a few examples of what to expect.\n\n* misc. servers and comput
 ers equipment * misc. antiquated hardware * ethernet switches * sever racks
  * ham radios * capacitors * audio equipment * peripherals * cameras / micr
 oscopes * wifi equipment * lights * extension cords!! * mouse (mice) * myst
 ery box! * UPS * old and new TVs * high voltage power supplies * tools * ga
 me systems * electrical equipment * etc.\n\nSELL YOUR STUFF!\n\nFor those c
 onsidering setting up a table or taking a space at this community event\, w
 e are asking for a $10 dollars donation and welcome any other donations (ca
 sh or items). We will have tables for you to use\, but space will be limite
 d (first come\, first serve)\, but you are welcome to bring your own table.
 \n\nMembers and participants are encouraged to park in the back near the ga
 rage.\n\nIf you're interested in table space\, please contactinfo@unallocat
 edspace.org or me with the subject line "SWAP MEET SETUP".\n\nPLEASE SHARE!
LAST-MODIFIED:20171216T232911Z
SEQUENCE:1
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Tech Swap Meet
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
