DESCRIPTION:Please let us know you're attending at http://meetu.ps/2RCqn2 .
 \n\nMMARC hosts an annual hamfest near the end of January at the Odenton Ba
 ptist Church 8410 Piney Orchard Pkwy\, Odenton\, MD 21113 for one time in J
 an 2016\, then returns to the Odenton Fire Hall in 2017. The 2016 hamfest w
 ill be held on Saturday January 30. The price for a table is $15 for the 20
 16 hamfest\, for more information contact Frank n3seo@aol.com.\n\nTalk in i
 s on the 146.805- repeater with tone 107.2.\n\nFood and drink will be avail
 able to purchase.\n\nAmateur radio license exams are available at the hamfe
 st. Preregistration is requested\, but walk-ins are welcome. Website: https
 ://sites.google.com/site/marylandmobileers/hamfests-1/hamfest-2\n\nSponsor:
  Maryland Mobileers Amateur Radio Club\nType: ARRL Hamfest\nTalk-In: 146.80
 5/146.205 (PL 107.2)\n
LAST-MODIFIED:20171216T232911Z
LOCATION:8410 Piney Orchard Pkwy\, Odenton\, MD 21113\, USA
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:HamFest Maryland Mobileers Amateur Radio Club
TRANSP:OPAQUE
