UID:joij5qf7qua4s7ktv8ogu4j8m8@google.com
CREATED:20171216T230211Z
DESCRIPTION:We will be cleaning/improving the space from 2pm to 6pm. Everyo
 ne is always welcome to come and stop by. We will be firing up the LAN Part
 y around 6ish and running all night and into Sunday! No need to leave at ni
 ght\, sleep on the floor\, bring a bedroll\, wake up and game some more!\n\
 n\nSo please join us all\, and prepare to be there a while!\nGames to be pl
 ayed and we ask you have everything patched are:\n\nUT2004 Patch:3369\nTeam
  Fortress 2\nLeft 4 Dead 2\nSerious Sam 3\nLeague of Legions (Levels Under 
 5)\nQuake 3 Arena\nBattlefield 3\nCall Of Duty\nMW3\nMinecraft\nAnd anythin
 g else you want to play\n\n\nJust a reminder that everyone is to patch and 
 get all their downloads done BEFORE the LAN! Got a crappy internet at home.
  NO PROBLEM! Swing by Friday night and I'll personally help you get all pat
 ched up and downloaded. Second No mass downloading. During the LAN we ask t
 hat you only use the internet for basic IM chat\, smaller patches and gener
 al web surfing. A lot of games need it to be able to play smooth and the po
 int of the event is gaming. UAS Staff reserves the right to check ALL compu
 ters for downloading STEAM clients\, Torrent\, and the like. Last but most 
 important... Patch your OS and anti-virus.\n\n\nAs always the events are fr
 ee to attend but electricity and having the space costs money\, please dona
 te!\nSuggested Donation $10-20
LAST-MODIFIED:20171216T232911Z
LOCATION:Unallocated Space\, 512 Shaw Court #105\, Severn\, MD 21144
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:LAN Party
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
