UID:jooohj76ikk9r59uhqbm604408@google.com
CREATED:20171216T230211Z
DESCRIPTION:Yes\, we're bringing you another epic twelve hours of gaming an
 d fragging fun!!\n\nBring a dish or snacks to share\, if you wish\, and we'
 ll have a spread for lunch and snacking! We'll likely order pizza around th
 e dinner hour\, so bring $5-10 to get in on that action. \n\nWe already too
 k a short poll of games / interests\, but if you didn't participate\, we're
  still interested in your preferences and opinions. It's quick and painless
 \, I promise! \;-) \n\nBring your gaming rig\, whether laptop or desktop\, 
 your **UPDATED** games/clients/OS\, potluck item(s)\, and an appetite for d
 estruction and mayhem (virtual\, that is.) \n\nSchedule: \n\n  12pm - 2pm S
 etup\n\n  2pm - 5pm Free Play (we'll see what people are interested in) \n\
 n  5pm - 6pm Minecraft Hunger Games Style Deathmatch\n\n  6pm FOOD!!!!!!!!!
 !!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!! \n\n  6pm ~ 7pm TBD To
