DESCRIPTION:Yes\, it's that time of the month again.   Ham Radio Night! Fri
 day July \n5th\, from 6-ish pm until we get done.. \n\nThis month we will d
 iscuss what we learned on Field day and how we can \nimprove for next year.
   We made a big splash with a lot of hype for \nUnallocated Space with this
  event and I will be addressing that as well \nto see how we can capitalize
  on it. \n\nWe also have Pictures!!!  (Thanks to Mike!) \n\nAlso now that F
 ield day is complete\, we will discuss other projects that \nwe'd like to d
 o in the coming months as well. 
