DESCRIPTION:It's that time of year again! The time of year where we roll up
  our sleeves  and CLEAN THE SPACE! We will be focusing on cleaning the memb
 er storage space up in the loft and processing the donation bins!  Our goal
  is for members to come in and reconnect with old projects and rekindle the
  passion they had for that project\, take the project home or possibly dona
 te it to the out pile so some one else can use the parts. We are doing this
  so that other members will have a chance to keep projects here and colaber
 ate with others. Also we are going to tidy up the HAM shack. We will be ord
 er pizza around noon for lunch and have music while cleaning so please come
  join us!
