 ent includes some of the following activities:\n\n- Building with LEGOs! \n
 - Discover with LEGOs! \n- Swapping LEGOs! \n- Drinks & Snacks @ 4pm (Juice
 \, Soda\, Fruit\, Animal Crackers) *no charge\n\nLEGO Day is also a great o
 pportunity to:\n\n- Show Off Your Designs - Discuss LEGO Events / Communiti
 es \n- Donate LEGOs to Unallocated Space (for Future Events)\n\nPlease join
  us by RSVPing at http://www.meetup.com/Unallocated-Space/events/161664602/
  
