DESCRIPTION:The Minicon is a event carried over from one of our original fo
 unders to share knowledge and projects.  This event is designed for anyone 
 to share in presentations between 15 minutes and 1 hour some knowledge.  Gi
 ven the diverse nature of this community\, most any topic/project will be o
 f someone's interest.  This is also a great opportunity to test a conferenc
 e presentation.  \n\n\nFor a list of topics that have been requested and pr
 evious presentations\, see http://www.unallocatedspace.org/uas/minicon/\n\n
 Please send a message to Forgotten if your interested in sharing.  This eve
 nt relies on volunteers otherwise it will get pushed back.  Thank you for c
 ontributing!\n\n
LAST-MODIFIED:20171216T232911Z
