CREATED:20171216T230211Z
DESCRIPTION:Come out and help with this month's Space Improvement Day\, THI
 S Saturday\, Jan 25 from noon to six.\n\nPlease try to drop by with a helpi
 ng hand. We could really use help in moving\, organizing\, cleaning\, clear
 ing\, and making the space better for your future visits.\n\nThis month's s
 pace improvement day will actually involve swapping the storage and hangout
  areas\, and as we do that we'll be looking to better organize our storage 
 setup.\n\nThis event is perfect for those looking to get more involved or f
 or those looking to make a difference. It's going to be a lot of work\, so 
 we can really use all hands on deck!\n\nWonko will be taking point on the o
 verall move and transition to the new setup. Usako (that's me) will be taki
 ng point on sorting and organizing all our stuff before it moves to the new
  storage location. Buddy will be taking point on clean up and probably help
 ing direct people to where they can help as the day goes on.\n\nThis is goi
 ng to be a big group effort\, and YOU can be a BIG help! \;-) So\, come out
  whenever and for however long as you can\, and help us improve Unallocated
  Space!
LAST-MODIFIED:20171216T232911Z
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Space Improvement Day
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
