CREATED:20171216T230211Z
DESCRIPTION:Join us at Unallocated for an evening of fragging goodness!! A 
 wide variety of games will be loaded up and played until nary a headshot re
 mains!!!\n\nOur Favorites:\n\nUnreal Tournament 2004 : Patch 3369\nTeam For
 tress 2\nLeft 4 Dead 2\nCounter Strike Source\nCounter Strike 1.6\nSerious 
 Sam 3\nLeague of Legends/Dota2 (if your in the beta)\nQuake 3 Arena\nCall o
 f Duty MW3\nBorderlands 2\n\nGiven its Halloween\, we will have candy\, cos
 tumes and good fun. I hope to see you there! This event is potluck style fo
 r food/drinks\, bring something.\n\nThis event is free\, but to help pay co
 sts of rent\, power and cooling\, please consider donating $10-$20.
