DESCRIPTION:This event will be an evening of food\, drink\, beer\, games\, 
 movies\, mini CTF\, lights\, music\, and of course\, a fire tornado. If you
  like having fun and meeting people\, then this event is for you (and free)
 !  FYI: We will not be permitting hard liquor \n\nLet’s talk food and drink
 . You're thinking bacon\, right? Or maybe homemade sweet potato pie. I hear
  folks love kabobs. The grill is going to be working overtime. What you’re 
 bringing is entirely up to you. This is you’re opportunity to show off that
  special recipe and that fancy pants imported beer. Please see the attached
  Google Doc spreadsheet to see what others are bringing to the p. We look f
 orward to seeing you. Please contact info@unallocatedspace.org if you have 
 any questions/concerns.\n\nhttps://docs.google.com/spreadsheet/ccc?key=0Avq
 XQ2p0sEvCdHhEZEltY2JIZDNERU9vWDh3X2otZlE\n\nScheduled Activities\n\n·      
  12:00pm – 1:00pm - Open House / Pizza\, Snacks\, & Drinks\n·       1:00pm 
 – 3:00pm - Analog Games\n·       3:00pm – 5:00pm - Mini CTF\n·       3:00pm
  – 5:00pm - Plasma Speaker\n·       3:00pm – 5:00pm - Xbox 360 Just Dance w
 \\ Kinect\n·       5:00pm - Announce the Mini CTF Winners\n·       5:00pm –
  Midnight - Grill / Potluck Food & Drinks\n·       7:00pm (Sunset) – Midnig
 ht - Outside Movie (Short Circuit 1 & 2)\n·       7:00pm – Midnight - Laser
  Lights & Music\n·       7:30pm – Fire Tornado
