DESCRIPTION:Agenda\n1. Operational Amplifiers (voltage feedback only)\n2. D
 igital to Analog Conversion (R2R Ladder)\n3. Sampling Audio With Arduino\n\
 nRequired Items\n1. Laptop (Needs to have an audio jack)\n2. Arduino (Any k
 ind will do)\n3. Breadboard\n4. Jumper wires\n5. USB cable for your Arduino
 \n\nProvided Items\n1. Operational Amplifier\n2. Audio cable\n3. Resistors 
 (2K ohm)\n4. Small speakers\n\nIf you need any items in the required items 
 section\, please E-Mail uas.arduino@gmail.com. We have a few of all of the 
 required items\, but we need to know how many to prepare.\n\nSince the spac
 e runs off of donations\, we would like to mention that the recommended don
 ation for this class is $10. It is by no means a requirement! Attendance to
  the space\, and this class\, is 100% free to all!
