 ormation Packet:\n  http://www.arrl.org/files/file/Field-Day/2013/2013%20FD
 %20Packet%20Version%202.pdf\n\nI would encourage all to take a look and may
 be even print it before coming to the meeting as we will be discussing opti
 ons that we can do for field day and put together an initial point target. 
 \n\nSome of the Field day topics we will discuss include: \n  Location\, Lo
 cation\, Location\n  Get-On-The-Air (GOTA) Station\n  How many Transmitters
  will we have? \n  How to rig the Antennae?\n  How will we power the equipm
 ent? \n  How to handle Public access? \n  How to keep the Public Busy?
