DESCRIPTION:I would like to invite Unallocated Space to exhibit at our inau
 gural Lego event " Brick Nation." \nAbout Brick Nation\n\nBrick Nation\, a 
 Lego Fan event for enthusiast of all ages\, is being\ncreated to increase a
 wareness of the fact that science\, technology\,\nengineering\, and mathema
 tics (STEM) are all in play when it comes to\nLEGO and other construction t
 oys. Creative arts\, the sometimes\nforgotten form of education\, can be ex
 pressed with LEGO. Families will\nparticipate in unique Lego building activ
 ities and attractions. There\nwill be building competitions and vendors fro
 m across the country. All\nproceeds from the door will go to The Wounded Wa
 rrior Project this\nevent is our preferred platform for giving back to our 
 community and\nhonoring those who protect us.\n\nBrick Nation is a 2 day ev
 ent which will be hosted at\nNorth Laurel Community Center\n9411 Whiskey Bo
 ttom Rd\, Laurel\, MD 20723\n\nPublic show-time hours will be\nSaturday Nov
 ember  15th 10:30AM to 4:00PM\nAnd\nSunday November  16th from 10:00am to 2
 PM\n\nUnallocated Space is a technology-based community center and\nwe are 
 trying to showcase science\, technology\,engineering\, and \nmathematics in
  different ways and I think Unallocated Space would be a good fit for the s
 how.\n\nIf you have any questions please feel free to e-mail me.\nThanks\nT
 odd\nbricknationmd@gmail.com\nbricknationmd.com
LAST-MODIFIED:20171216T232911Z
LOCATION:North Laurel Community Center 9411 Whiskey Bottom Rd\, Laurel\, MD
  20723
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Brick Nation
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
