DESCRIPTION:The Minicon is a time block dedicated to sharing knowledge\, te
 sting conference presentations and improving presentation skills.  The 4 ho
 ur block is broken up into a bunch of folks lasting between 15 minutes and 
 an hour\n\nForgotten am looking for speakers who want to test conference pr
 esentations\, share some knowledge\, and/or practice their speaking skills.
   Length is between 15 minutes and 1 hour.  Projector is available\, but yo
 u don't need slides if you prefer not to.  I have some suggestions and a hi
 storical record of talks which may give you some ideas at the following URL
 :\n\nhttp://www.unallocatedspace.org/uas/minicon\n\nWe need your help to ma
 ke this event a success.  Regardless of what your experience is in\, there 
 are people who will almost always find it interesting to learn about.
