DESCRIPTION:TOPIC: RaspberryPi Hacking/INFOSEC Projects\nSUMMARY: There are
  lots of cool projects on various flavors of RaspberryPis that we can try t
 alk about or give feedback on. Anything and everything from using a Pi Zero
  to make a Usb Injection tool to a makeshift Angry Access Point to a rogue 
 network device. Bring your ideas bring your after action reports and let’s 
 all learn about some cool projects we can go home and try or definitely not
  try. I will specifically go over two projects I am working on\, and two I 
 want to work on and the rest will be discussion and other people sharing pr
 ojects.\nSKILL LEVEL: Everyone\nPRESENTER: Wasabi\n\nhttps://www.meetup.com
 /Unallocated-Space/events/241727266/
