DESCRIPTION:A note from Proto:  Sorry everyone\, but I have to cancel the A
 rduino Night tonight.  I've come down with some illness that is mauling my 
 throat.  We'll try again next week.\n\nUPDATE: For those who are interested
 \, several members will be at the space tonight for an impromptu Show and T
 ell night. We’ll talk about our projects\, help answer questions and share 
 cool ideas. Stop in and get your weekly Arduino fix!
