DESCRIPTION:Hey all\, It's that time once again to roll up our sleeves and 
 give the space some TLC. I meant to get the word out earlier\, but I'm look
 ing at this coming Saturday June 6th unless there isn't enough response.\n\
 nHere's the deal:\n\nJune 6th\, 10am\, we'll be hitting the following thing
 s:\n\n - Wiping down tables.\n - Cleaning floors.\n - Cleaning fridge/micro
 wave as needed.\n - Cleaning bathrooms.\n - Tidying work areas and storage 
 area.\n    - The storage/networking area has gotten disorganized. Things ne
 ed put back in place.\n - Moving things to the outpile as appropriate.\n   
   - If we have enough hands on deck\, someone can pull outdated books from 
 the library.\n\nPlease RSVP to the meetup ( http://meetu.ps/2JJvNK ) or her
 e (if you don't use meetup)\, so we know how much help we'll have.\n\nThank
 s for your support!\n~Usako~
