BEGIN:VEVENT
DTSTART:20160415T230000Z
DTEND:20160416T020000Z
DTSTAMP:20250626T025311Z
UID:r3tummch63k2peo64rhu3gafk8@google.com
CREATED:20171216T230211Z
DESCRIPTION:Topic: Improvements to the Zumobot\n\nThe Zumobot will be going
  to RobotFest\, but it needs much more awesome.\n\nPrimarily I will be work
 ing on these tasks for the robot and will be talking about different aspect
 s of how to do the following.\n\n-xBee\n     -mesh vs point to point\n     
 -received signal strength\n\n-Viewing data from Arduino with Processing\n  
    -Serial\n     -Draw\n     -hopefully a simple compass graphic\n\n-The Ad
 afruit BNO055 9-DOF module\n\nThis will be more open discussion than lectur
 e.\n\nThings to bring:\nAt this point the robot knows/will know it's orient
 ation in the world\, but nothing about the world it inhabits. If you are in
 terested please bring any sensors (as simple as limit switches) and help to
  add them to the robot.
