 ts prepare for and pass the OSCP exam and more generally develop their skil
 ls in pentesting. The goal is to share our own experience\, resources\, and
  methodologies to improve our abilities as a whole.\n\nOur group also likes
  to compete in local and online CTF's and welcome those interested in doing
  hands on activities to improve their abilities in cybersecurity.
