DESCRIPTION:Usako will be hosting an awesome evening of gaming and fragging
  and fragging gaming. There will even be a space bridge simulator involved\
 , and if you're feeling like a bit of extra fun - feel free to come dressed
  for your role on the ship. Come and join us as we simulate our very own US
 S UAS in the game Artemis.\n\nCome on down\, have a cold beverage and kill 
 some zombies\, fly a spacecraft\, or conquer the world. Whatever your game\
 , it's sure to be a fun filled evening of epic proportions.\n\nSome of the 
 games you can expect:\n\nArtemis / Team Fortress 2 / Left 4 Dead 2 / Diablo
  3 / Portal 2 / Counter Strike / Civilization V / Doom / Doom 2 / League of
  Legends / Defense of the Ancients 2\n\n*****PLEASE EVERYONE UPDATE STEAM/G
 AMES AHEAD OF TIME!!!*****\n\nWe'll also have Mumble running locally for co
 mms\, if you want them. http://mumble.sourceforge.net/\n\n\nFOOD: There wil
 l be grilling of dogs and burgers or pizza for sure. Bring some snackage an
 d/or beverage to share if you would like. I'll be bringing the Cider. :D 
LAST-MODIFIED:20171216T232911Z
LOCATION:Unallocated Space
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:EPIC LAN PARTY
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
