DESCRIPTION:Charlie and Surefire will be leading a discussion on getting a 
 permanent ham shack at UAS.  A substantial part of this process is mounting
  an antenna (in the attic\, on the roof\, or on a detached tower).  In addi
 tion\, we would like to plan a dedicated ham radio desk in the upstairs lof
 t\, which will involve cleaning up\, running power\, and building/acquiring
  furniture.  All of this is open for discussion.\n\nWe need to come up with
  a plan and pass the details to the landlord.  By the end of the evening\, 
 we should have a handful of detailed options\, with logistics\, pricing and
  photos.\n\nNo need to RSVP.  Just swing by.  We'll do a Papa John's order 
 part-way-through.
LAST-MODIFIED:20171216T232911Z
LOCATION:Unallocated Space
SEQUENCE:1
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Ham Radio Antenna Discussion
