DESCRIPTION:Join the UAS Ham Radio club for the ham radio event of the year
 !  UAS will be at the North American Trade Schools facility in Security Squ
 are Mall for this 24-hour non-stop event.  In addition to ham radio activit
 ies\, we'll be promoting the space to the general public\, providing educat
 ional presentations for anyone who is interested\, and helping new folks ge
 t on the air.\n\nWe'll have laptops\, radios\, antennas\, generators and al
 l the gear set up Friday afternoon.  Saturday afternoon\, the event will st
 art and we'll be contacting stations around the world\, earning points usin
 g voice\, digital and morse code-based communication.  Finally\, Sunday eve
 ning\, we'll say our goodbyes and start tearing down.\n\nInterested?  Conta
 ct the UAS Ham Radio club at hamradio@unallocatedspace.org.
LAST-MODIFIED:20171216T232911Z
LOCATION:North American Trade Schools\, 6901 Security Blvd #16\, Baltimore\
 , MD
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Ham Radio Field Day
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
END:VEVENT
