UID:snu5ioji146pi3r0vpruh81kpc@google.com
CREATED:20171216T230211Z
DESCRIPTION:As three-time finalists in the Maryland Cyber-Challenge\, havin
 g\ncompeted in Ghost-in-the-Shellcode\, Scram\, a CDCC participate\, and\nh
 osting two competitions of its own\, Unallocated has been active in\nCaptur
 e-the-Flag (CTF) competitions since the space's inception. This\nis the fir
 st monthly meeting for people interested to get together\,\nlearn\, organiz
 e\, and prepare to compete in these challenges.\nAnyone that has participat
 ed\, is participating\, or wants to\nparticipate in a Unallocated CTF team 
 should attend. No experience\nnecessary\, though prepare to learn under fir
 e!\n\nTopics covered:\n - CTFs for the Curious!\n - Where we are with CTF36
 5 and our future plans\n - Upcoming CTFs: RuCTFE (Dec 14th 5am-2pm (Eastern
 ) - day before this event)\, GITSc (January)\, UnalloCTF (Q1 2014)
LAST-MODIFIED:20171216T232911Z
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:CTF Meeting
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
