CLASS:PUBLIC
CREATED:20171216T230211Z
DESCRIPTION:Motor control with H-Bridge\n\nPlease bring your computer\, Ard
 uino\, and small breadboard.\n\nMotors\, transistors\, and ICs will be prov
 ided.\n\nIf you have a motor(s) you are trying to get running that doesn't 
 sink a whole lot of current please bring them as well.  We may not get them
  working but I'm sure we can release some magic blue smoke trying.\n\nThe p
 resentation will not run for the full time. There will be ample time to exp
 eriment with what we just learned. Feel free to bring any other projects yo
 u are working on. If you need help\, great. If you just want to show off wh
 at you are working on we would love to see it.\n\nWe run entirely from dona
 tions. This is a free event. A suggested donation of $10 is appreciated. Pl
 ease help keep the hacks rolling (on Arduino controlled wheels).
