UID:ugdhaqm6ph4kulirl5t8epfc60@google.com
CREATED:20171216T230211Z
DESCRIPTION:Topic: Adding a controller/joystick to your Robot\n\nAgenda:\n7
 :00 - 8:00)\nProcessing and Joystick Input\n\n8:00 - 9:00)\nRefresher on mo
 tor control\nConverting joystick input to motor speed\nto Map() or not to M
 ap()?\nThinking about speed and direction\nServo and Stepper motors\n\n9:00
  - 10:00: \nCurrent state of the Zumobot\nConstructive playtime (show off w
 hat you are working on)\n\nThis class will be more discussion and open topi
 c oriented and may not hold to the times listed on the syllabus. The goal i
 s to adapt the topics to the specific controller needs for your project.\n\
 nWhat to bring:\nLaptop with Arduino software installed.\nIf you have Proce
 ssing installed it will also be helpful: https://processing.org/download/?p
 rocessing\n\nIf you have a USB Joystick or gamepad please bring it.\nPlease
  bring any project(s) you are working on to show off or get help with
