CREATED:20171216T230211Z
DESCRIPTION:**You're invited to the Unallocated Space’s Six Year Anniversar
 y Party!\n\n**On Saturday\, November 5\, 2016\, please join Unallocated Spa
 ce to celebrate 6 years of providing the community a place to Teach\, Learn
 \, Build.\n\nWe've achieved so much and brought together so many people. It
 's time to relax with friends\, play games\, enjoy watching a movie or list
 ening to music\, share some good food and drink\, and of course\, behold ou
 r famous fire tornado. If you like having fun and meeting people with simil
 ar interests\, then this event is for you!\n\n+ Location:\n\nUnallocated Sp
 ace\n512 Shaw Ct Ste 105\nSevern\, MD 21144\n\n+ Scheduled Activities:\n\n-
  12PM to 3PM - Open House / Analog Board Game\n- 3PM - Midnight - Music\, M
 usic\, Music!!!\n- 3PM to 6PM - Table Flipping & 50/50 Raffle\n- 4PM - Boar
 d Announcements\n- 5PM - Food & Drinks\n- 7PM - Winner Announcements\n- 8PM
  - Fire Tornado\n\n+ Food & Drink:\n\nLet’s talk about food and drink. The 
 grill is going to be working overtime. We will be conducting a potluck and 
 this is your opportunity to show off your culinary skills and fancy importe
 d beer. Please help us by updating the Google Doc with the food and drink y
 ou will be contributing.\n\nhttps://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1_dC23GI
 dl4-WvHXcbLEqu1XXSkvOlUewom86KDmGwf8/edit?usp=sharing\n\n+ Registration:\n\
 nhttp://meetu.ps/e/C0wzj/bkJ5K/d\n\nSee you there!
LAST-MODIFIED:20171216T232911Z
LOCATION:Unallocated Space\, 512 Shaw Ct #105\, Severn\, MD 21144\, USA
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Unallocated Space’s 6th Anniversary Party
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
