DESCRIPTION:THIS EVENT IS NOT AT THE SPACE!\nCome join W3UAS at the CQ Worl
 dwide DX Contest up at North American Trade Schools in Security Square Mall
 \, right off I-695 just north of I-70.\nCome by at any time during the even
 t and make radio contacts from around the world! Everyone is welcome\, lice
 nsed or not.\nPlease contact Corey (ckoval7[at]gmail[dot]com) or Charlie (c
 wfullerton21043[at]gmail[dot]com) ahead of time to get into the school.\nTh
 e VHF talk-in frequency is 146.555 MHz \nMode:  SSB\nBands: 160\, 80\, 40\,
  20\, 15\, 10m\nI hope to see you there!
LAST-MODIFIED:20171216T232911Z
