 onnectivity\n     5. VGA breakout (red\, green\, blue\, horizontal sync\, v
 ertical sync\, and ground) if you do not have a VGA connector on your dev b
 oard.\n\nProvided Items:\n     1. VGA breakout if you let the instructor kn
