 n this hands-on-keys session we will explore different types of competition
 s\, from capture-the-flag to offense/defense and everything in between and 
 take a crack at some challenges. This is a joint event hosted by Unallocate
 d Space and Women's Society of Cyberjutsu\, and is open to all.\nGOAL: Deve
 lop cyber competition skills and methodologies.\nWHAT TO BRING:  Your lapto
 p and enthusiasm. Also\, you'll want to grab the materials here: https://ct
 f4noobs.cover6solutions.com\nSKILL LEVEL:  Everyone\nPRESENTER: Marcelle @M
