DESCRIPTION:<span>The Unallocated Space Minicon is an event with scheduled 
 time blocks dedicated to sharing knowledge\, testing presentations and impr
 oving presentation skills. Unallocated Space is looking for speakers who wa
 nt to test conference presentations\, share some knowledge\, and/or practic
 e their speaking skills. We need your help to make this event a success. Re
 gardless of what your experience is in\, there are people who will almost a
 lways find it interesting to learn about. For suggestions and a historical 
 record of past and current talks for inspiration\, please visit our Minicon
  presences at&nbsp\;</span><a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=http%3A%2F
 %2Fwww.unallocatedspace.org%2Fuas%2Fminicon&amp\;sa=D&amp\;usd=2&amp\;usg=A
 FQjCNFpZPeXhqvmCEWaRGOejzAJWNBtBQ" title="http://www.unallocatedspace.org/u
 as/minicon" target="_blank">http://www.unallocatedspace.org/uas/minicon</a>
 <br><br><span>Presentations can be any length up to 1 hour. Projector is av
 ailable\, but you don't need slides if you prefer not to.</span><br><span><
 br></span><br><span>Presentations are volunteer focused. Please volunteer t
 o share your knowledge. Suggestions are available here:&nbsp\;</span><a hre
 f="https://www.google.com/url?q=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.unallocatedspace.org%2Fuas
 %2Fminicon&amp\;sa=D&amp\;usd=2&amp\;usg=AFQjCNFpZPeXhqvmCEWaRGOejzAJWNBtBQ
 " title="http://www.unallocatedspace.org/uas/minicon" target="_blank">http:
 //www.unallocatedspace.org/uas/minicon</a><span><br></span>
LAST-MODIFIED:20180304T054036Z
