DESCRIPTION:We’d like to invite you\, your family\, and friends to our comm
 unity tech swap meet / garage sale this Saturday\, June 9th 2018\, 7am-3pm\
 , rain or shine. The purpose of the sale is to clear space\, raise money fo
 r future projects\, and encourage the community to recycle.\nSee our Meetup
  announcement at https://www.meetup.com/Unallocated-Space/events/250544106/
  !\n\nLOCATION\n\nUnallocated Space\n512 Shaw Court\, Suite 105\nSevern\, M
 aryland 21144\n\nWHAT WILL YOU FIND?\n\nAnything is possible. Things to exp
 ect to see for sale will vary\, but here are a few examples of what to expe
 ct.\n\nmisc. servers and computers equipment * misc. antiquated hardware * 
 ethernet switches * ham radios * capacitors * audio equipment * peripherals
  * cameras / microscopes * WiFi equipment * lights * extension cords!! * ke
 yboards and mice * mystery boxes! * old and new TVs * high voltage power su
 pplies * tools * game systems * electrical equipment * etc.\n\nSELL YOUR ST
 UFF!\n\nFor those considering setting up a table or taking a space at this 
 community event\, we are asking for a $10 dollars donation and welcome any 
 other donations (cash or items). We will have tables for you to use\, but s
 pace will be limited (first come\, first serve)\, but you are welcome to br
 ing your own table.\nIf you’re interested in table space\, please contact i
 nfo (at) unallocatedspace (dot) org with the subject line “SWAP MEET SETUP”
 .
LAST-MODIFIED:20180517T215446Z
LOCATION:Unallocated Space\, 512 Shaw Court Unit 105\, Severn\, MD\, us\, 2
 1144
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Unallocated Space (UAS) Community Tech Swap Meet/Garage Sale (Anne 
 Arundel\, MD)
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
