 ill be hosting a competition night at Unallocated Space. This time the comp
 etition is the Cyberlympics qualifier we'll be working on is a 12-hour\, je
 opardy-style\, online CTF.\n\nExpect a number of challenge categories such 
 as Digital Forensics\, Network Exploitation\, Web Applications and Service 
 Exploitation.\n\nTeams need to be formed and registered by 7/31. Contact Ma
 rcelle if you are looking for a team to join. (marcelle.lee {at} womenscybe
 rjutsu {dot} org)\n\nFor more information\, please visit:\nhttps://www.cybe
 rlympics.org/about-the-games/schedule/\n\n\nWHAT TO BRING: Your laptop and 
