 g how to make acrylic pour paintings. Everyone will make their own painting
 . We will let them dry overnight and they can be picked up at a later date.
 \n\nGOAL: Make some really cool art together.\n\nWHAT TO BRING: Just be pre
 pared\, you may get paint on you or your clothing. If you have a smock or a
 pron\, you might want to bring that.\n\nAll art supplies will be provided f
 or a materials fee of $8 per person. \n\nIf you prefer to bring your own ca
 nvas and paints\, you are welcome to do so.\n\nWe will be painting a 12x12 
 canvas. Please see the link for examples of the type of painting we'll be c
 reating.\n\nExamples: https://www.facebook.com/pg/Unallocated/photos/?tab=a
 lbum&album_id=1943528225698773\n\n\nSKILL LEVEL: Everyone\n\nPRESENTER: Whi
 tney
