DESCRIPTION:Come out to Unallocated Space on September 1st for an 8 hour in
 troduction to Networking. We will explore the OSI Model as well as conduct 
 labs with Wireshark and Packet Tracer. By the end of this course you should
  have an understanding of a simple LAN that includes routers\, switches\, a
 nd firewalls.\n\nWhat you'll need:\nA notebook and pen\nA laptop with the f
 ollowing software installed:\n\nPacket Tracer: https://www.netacad.com/cour
 ses/packet-tracer\nWireshark https://www.wireshark.org/download.html\n\nI a
 lso recommend packing a lunch. 
LAST-MODIFIED:20180815T221137Z
LOCATION:Unallocated Space\, 512 Shaw Ct #105\, Severn\, MD 21144\, USA
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Networking 101 Boot camp
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
