DESCRIPTION:Course Description: ​This progressive\, hands-on course will co
 ver the fundamentals<br>of electronics\, including direct current (DC)\, al
 ternating current (AC)\, and<br>semiconductors. As we progress though the c
 ourse we'll build and analyze a variable DC power supply\, then build an au
 dio amplifier.<br><br>Instructor: Corey Koval (corey@unallocatedspace.org)<
 br><br>Required Materials:<br><ul><li>Notebook<br></li><li>Pen/Pencils<br><
 /li><li>Scientific Calculator<br></li><li>Variable DC power supply: <a href
 ="https://www.jameco.com/z/JE215-Dual-Output-Adjustable-Linear-Regulated-Po
 wer-Supply-Kit_20626.html">https://www.jameco.com/z/JE215-Dual-Output-Adjus
 table-Linear-Regulated-Power-Supply-Kit_20626.html</a> (DO NOT ASSEMBLE!)</
 li><li>Resistor assortment <a href="http://www.digikey.com/product-detail/e
 n/RS125/RS125-ND/7108">http://www.digikey.com/product-detail/en/RS125/RS125
 -ND/7108</a><br></li><li>Digital Multimeter: <a href="http://www.circuitspe
 cialists.com/digital-multimeter-csi2010.html">http://www.circuitspecialists
 .com/digital-multimeter-csi2010.html</a><br></li><li>Breadboard <a href="ht
 tp://www.circuitspecialists.com/wb-102+j.html">http://www.circuitspecialist
 s.com/wb-102+j.html</a><br></li><li>jumper wires (with and without alligato
 r clips) <a href="https://www.circuitspecialists.com/m000f0002.html">https:
 //www.circuitspecialists.com/m000f0002.html</a><br></li><li>Magnifying glas
 s if you need one to see up close<br></li></ul><br><br><br>Course Outline<b
 r>Topic #1: DC: ​definitions\, voltage\, current\, electrons\, how electron
 s flow\, Ohm’s<br>law\, resistors\, resistor color code\, resistor dividers
 \, series circuits\, parallel<br>circuits\, series-parallel circuits\, powe
 r\, diodes\, switches and circuit protection\,<br>capacitors\, inductors<br
 >Topic #2: AC: ​frequency\, waveforms\, capacitors\, capacitive reactance\,
 <br>inductors\, inductive reactance\, impedance\, RLC circuits\, transforme
 rs\, rectifiers\,<br>voltage regulators<br>Topic #3: Semiconductors: ​trans
 istors\, amplifiers
LAST-MODIFIED:20180921T000333Z
LOCATION:Unallocated Space\, 512 Shaw Ct #105\, Severn\, MD 21144\, USA
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Electronics Fundamentals Orientation Day
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
