DESCRIPTION:**You’re invited to the Unallocated Space’s 8th Anniversary Par
 ty!\n\nThe time is upon us again. It’s time to celebrate our successes with
  all our friends and patrons! Unallocated Space (UAS) cordially invites eve
 ryone to join us on Saturday\, November 3rd\, 2018 to celebrating 8 years o
 f providing the community a place to teach\, learn\, and build.\n\nExpect c
 opious amounts of food\, drink\, people\, and music. What would be an UAS P
 arty without a fire tornado ⸮ (Percontation Point: U+2E2E) Thank goodness y
 ou don’t need to ponder this too long. There will be an epic fire tornado a
 nd camp fire.\n\nAlso we are excited about updating you on the good things 
 we’ve been up to and love to thank all those outstanding individuals who’ve
  contributed to the space this year by making a few exciting announcements 
 and changes within UAS.\n\n**If you like having fun and meeting people with
  similar interests\, then this event is for you!\nDate/Time: Saturday\, Nov
 ember 3rd\, 2018 / 4PM–12AM\nLocation: Unallocated Space\, 512 Shaw Ct Ste 
 105\, Severn\, MD 21144\n\n**We will be conducting a potluck and this is yo
 ur opportunity to show off your culinary skills and fancy imported beer. Pl
 ease help us by updating our Google Doc with the food and drinks you’re bri
 nging. http://goo.gl/o3Z98g\n\n**We look forward to seeing you there!\n\n**
 Please RSVP at https://www.meetup.com/Unallocated-Space/events/254915134/ .
 \n\n===\n\nFrequently Asked Questions:\n\n(Q) What is the scheduled activit
 ies? (A)\n– 3PM – 4PM – Pre-Party Shenanigans\n– 4PM – Music\, 50/50 Raffle
 \, & Fund Raiser\n– 5PM – Food & Drinks\n– 6PM – Board Announcements\n– 6PM
  – Fire Tornado (Round 1)\n– 7PM – Raffle Winner Announcements\n– 7PM – Fir
 e Tornado (Round 2)\n– 8PM-12AM – Camp-Style Fire\n\n(Q) Who is invited? (A
 ) Everyone! Twitter: “RT @Unallocated Space (of Severn\, MD) is having its 
 8 Year Anniversary Party #hackerspace on Sat\, Nov 3rd\, 2018. Please join 
 us and RSVP!https://www.unallocatedspace.org/2018/09/22/unallocated-spaces-
 8th-anniversary-party-nov-3rd/“\n\n(Q) Who is UAS? (A) Unallocated Space is
  a 501(c)(3) Non-profit Hackerspace. Our mission is to foster creative and 
 technical growth through open collaboration by providing tools and resource
 s within the greater Baltimore-Washington Metro area. Learn more at http://
 www.unallocatedspace.org .\n\n(Q) How to support UAS? (A) Unlike most hacke
 rspaces\, all of our events\, classes\, and workshops are completely open t
 o the general public for free. We have continued to serve the community in 
 this manner for seven years. You can find more about donating and volunteer
 ing at http://www.unallocatedspace.org .
LAST-MODIFIED:20180922T190253Z
LOCATION:Unallocated Space\, 512 Shaw Ct #105\, Severn\, MD 21144\, USA
SEQUENCE:1
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Unallocated Space’s 8th Anniversary Party (Nov 3rd)
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
