UID:cdgjgcpl6hj38b9ncgpj6b9kcdj3ibb26gs3abb670pmac1m70sjacr664@google.com
CREATED:20180907T031256Z
DESCRIPTION:Halloween & Horror Epic LAN Party\, October 13th!! 12 HOURS of 
 Haunting Good Fun from noon til midnight!!\n\nWe knew you were dying to com
 e play some horror-themed games with us this October\, and we didn't want t
 o disappoint!\n\nSaturday\, October 13\, from noon until midnight we will b
 e running another epic 12-hour LAN party -- this time horror-themed!\n\nWe'
 ve got some other fun things in mind too! We'll have a costume contest for 
 those so inclined to dress up\, a hot seat tournament\, and a prize for the
  best themed food brought to share. \;-D\n\nGames you should bring (and upd
 ate beforehand):\n\n - L4D2\n - Dead Realm\n - Minecraft\n - Killing Floor\
 n - Deceit (F2P)\n - Dead by Daylight\n - Overwatch (Halloween Event!)\n\nI
 f you have some other favorite horror games you'd like to suggest\, please 
 do!\n\nFor the main food\, we encourage you to bring your favorite themed (
 or non-themed) dish / snacks to share. Later in the night\, we'll be orderi
 ng pizza so please bring some cash for that.\n\nWe'll be jammin' some aweso
 me on-theme beats for the event. So\, come out and get spooky with us! \;-D
 \n\nAs always\, this event is free\, but running the space is not. So\, we 
 do ask that you consider making a donation to help us continue providing yo
 u with epic fun events like this!
LAST-MODIFIED:20180930T032619Z
LOCATION:Unallocated Space\, 512 Shaw Ct #105\, Severn\, MD 21144\, USA
SEQUENCE:1
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Halloween & Horror Epic LAN Party
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
