DESCRIPTION:Classic Video Gaming Day-\n\nThis is an event that is focused o
 n console gaming. NES\, SNES\, N64\, PS\, Dreamcast etcetera.\n\nThe Idea c
 ame about because a bunch of friends were sitting around at a party and jon
 esing for some retro social gaming. So blow the dust off you favorite conso
 le and games. Bring some extra controllers and a spare TV if you can and jo
 in us for a day of gaming.\n\nCold Turkey Goldeneye Tournament- No prep pic
 kup the controller and go Tournament.\n\nMario Kart Tournament.\n\n\nPlay t
 ile you Die. RPGs you play till you die or 20mins\, what ever comes first\,
  then hand off the controller to the next person. Zelda Link to the Past\, 
 Chrono Trigger\, Secret of Mana and so on.
LAST-MODIFIED:20181011T015902Z
