DESCRIPTION:Open Shop is a time when we're open for anyone to come by and w
 ork on whatever they want. Our space and our tools will be available for yo
 u to work on anything you like\, be it electronics\, software\, 3D printing
 \, woodworking\, automotive work\, crafts\, hacking\, or anything else you 
 can imagine. Groups and individuals are equally welcome. Tools and space ar
 e available on a first-come\, first-serve basis\, so be courteous and share
  if you're using anything that is in-demand. If you want to use a piece of 
 equipment for your first time\, please reach out on our mailing list to fin
 d someone with experience that can help guide you so we can all be safe and
  keep our equipment in good shape for everyone.\n\nThis is also a great tim
 e for newcomers to the space to come check us out! Bring something to work 
 on or just check out the projects our members are working on.
LAST-MODIFIED:20181026T233233Z
LOCATION:Unallocated Space\, 512 Shaw Court #105\, Severn\, MD 21144\, Unit
 ed States
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Open Shop
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
