BEGIN:VEVENT
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20180118T190000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20180118T220000
DTSTAMP:20250626T025311Z
UID:mlgalfovor1a1pb2rdvamseabk@google.com
RECURRENCE-ID;TZID=America/New_York:20180118T190000
CREATED:20171216T230211Z
DESCRIPTION:TOPIC: INFOSEC NIGHT: General Q and A\n\nSUMMARY:  \nTonight we
  are going to talk about Information Security\, what specifically you may a
 sk? Well\, the answer is you tell us! There will be a few of us here to tak
 e your questions on all things technical and career oriented in infosec. Wa
 nt to know what we think you should focus on\, or what options you may have
  in a career? Want to know how to better protect your home? Want to know wh
 y Understudy thinks Windows sucks? Come by Unallocated and ask these questi
 ons and we will do our best to answer them.\nGOAL: To answer people's quest
 ions about the varied topics in infosec.\n\n\n\nWHAT TO BRING: You must bri
 ng questions\, otherwise it will be a lot of people sitting quietly in a ro
 om like detention with Ms. Wallabe in 4th grade\, and no on wants that\, es
 pecially me.\n\nSKILL LEVEL: Everyone\nPRESENTER: Understudy
LAST-MODIFIED:20181105T172403Z
LOCATION:Unallocated Space\, 512 Shaw Ct #105\, Severn\, MD 21144\, USA
SEQUENCE:1
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:INFOSEC Night: General Q and A
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20180201T190000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20180201T210000
DTSTAMP:20250626T025311Z
UID:mlgalfovor1a1pb2rdvamseabk@google.com
RECURRENCE-ID;TZID=America/New_York:20180201T190000
CREATED:20171216T230211Z
DESCRIPTION:<b>SPL103</b> – Splunk &gt\; Cleaning up Alerts / security even
 ts SUMMARY: Organizing Alerts in your SIEM. If you are still tracking alert
 s with a white board or sticky pads this talk might be beneficial.<br><br>G
 OAL: We are going over a free Splunk Tool called Alert Manager to help orga
 nize alerts and responses. This is a powerful tool that was designed with I
 TIL functions in mind.<br>Things to bring: Questions about Splunk or other 
 SIEM your familiar with.<br><br>SKILL LEVEL: Everyone<br><br>PRESENTER: JR
LAST-MODIFIED:20181105T172403Z
LOCATION:Unallocated Space\, 512 Shaw Ct #105\, Severn\, MD 21144\, USA
SEQUENCE:1
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:INFOSEC Night: Splunk SPL103
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
