RECURRENCE-ID;TZID=America/New_York:20180301T190000
CREATED:20171216T230211Z
DESCRIPTION:<b>SUMMARY</b>: We will cover the basics of Virtual Private Net
 working technology including types\, use cases\, and options for setting up
  your own.<br><br><b>GOAL</b>: Understand what using a VPN means and why yo
 u might want to use one.<br><br><b>SKILL LEVEL</b>: Everyone<br><br><b>PRES
 ENTER</b>: BobbyR
