 from a brief description of the underlying technology\, to the popular coin
 s and how to handle your coin securely. Please come with questions so that 
 I can get a general idea of the communities interests and the direction for
  future talks.\n\nGOAL: Gain a general understanding of the Blockchain spac
 e.\n\nThings to bring:  Questions and comments\n\n\nSKILL LEVEL:  Everyone\
 nPRESENTER: Blank
