UID:mlgalfovor1a1pb2rdvamseabk@google.com
RECURRENCE-ID;TZID=America/New_York:20180705T190000
CREATED:20171216T230211Z
DESCRIPTION:Description:\nThis talk is the second in a series of Red Team p
 resentations. Previously we discussed what Red Teaming was at a high level.
  This talk will discuss the first phases of any engagement\, which are the 
 Scoping phase and Enumeration phase. Often the beginning phases are discuss
 ed in courses and classes\, but never really explored in-depth. This talk w
 ill hopefully give more insight into these phases\, with a focus on scoping
  points of interest\, considerations\, and some live passive enumeration an
 d recon examples.\n\nGOAL:\nDiscuss the scoping phase and enumeration phase
  of a Red Team engagement\n\nThings to Bring:\n\nSUGGESTED:\nNote taking ma
 terials if you'd like to take notes as this will be mostly theory based. A 
 laptop or tablet if you'd like to follow along with the enumeration phase.\
 n\nSKILL LEVEL:\nEveryone. This presentation will continue a series of talk
 s reviewing basic Red Team Operations.\n\nPRESENTER:\nnyte
LAST-MODIFIED:20181105T172403Z
LOCATION:Unallocated Space\, 512 Shaw Ct #105\, Severn\, MD 21144\, USA
SEQUENCE:1
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:INFOSEC Night: Red Team 102
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
