DESCRIPTION:BrewCon 2018\n\nUnallocated Space is hosting its very first Bre
 wCon\, scheduled for Saturday\, November 10\, 2018.\n\nWhat is BrewCon?\n\n
 A day of talks and tastings from homebrewers and fermentation enthusiasts i
 n our community. Topics include: homebrewing\, winemaking\, fermentation\, 
 mixology / beverage crafting\, and more!\n\nSchedule:\n\nCheck out our 2018
  BrewCon Schedule: https://goo.gl/zasdXc\n\nTalks:\n\nThe 6 S's of Wine Tas
 ting\nWild Fermentation 101\nMead - If It's Sugar\, We'll Ferment It!\nEngi
 neering Up A Homebrewery\nLeveling Up Your Cocktails\nSake - Don't Throw Ou
 t That Moldy Rice!\n\nTastings:\n\nWild Fermented Pawpaw/Spicebush Berry Me
 ad\nMead (and More Mead)\nHomebrewed Beers/Ales\nLimoncello\nMakgeolli and 
 Kimchi\nSake\n\nAll of our events are free\, but keeping the lights on is n
 ot. We'd like to suggest a $5 donation for this event\, but it is not requi
 red.\n\nIf you'd like to learn about supporting the space by becoming a mem
 ber\, we've got a page just for you! -- https://www.unallocatedspace.org/me
 mbership/
LAST-MODIFIED:20181107T040737Z
LOCATION:Unallocated Space\, 512 Shaw Ct #105\, Severn\, MD 21144\, USA
SEQUENCE:2
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Brew Con
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
END:VEVENT
