 ford Crypto 1 Study Group is the event of the year for you! Together we wil
 l conquer the math and mystery of Crypto. Break down nerdy concepts into ev
 eryday concepts.<br><br>The Stanford Crypto 1 course is an online course pr
 ovided by Coursera. The course begins with a detailed discussion of how two
  parties who have<br>a shared secret key can communicate securely when a po
 werful adversary<br>eavesdrops and tampers with traffic. The second half of
