DESCRIPTION:**You’re invited to the Unallocated Space’s 9th Anniversary Par
 ty!<br><br>It’s time again for Saturday\, November 2nd\, 2019 to celebrate 
 9 years of providing the community a place to teach\, learn\, and build.<br
 ><br>Expect copious amounts of food\, drink\, people\, and music. What woul
 d be a UAS Party without a fire tornado?! We’ve got that problem solved wit
 h an epic fire tornado and campfire.<br><br>We are excited about updating y
 ou on the good things we’ve been up to and love to thank all those outstand
 ing individuals who’ve contributed to the space this year by making a few e
 xciting announcements and changes within UAS.<br><br>**If you like having f
 un and meeting people with similar interests\, then this event is for you!<
 br>Date/Time: Saturday\, November 2nd\, 2018 / 4PM–12AM<br>Location: Unallo
 cated Space\, 512 Shaw Ct Ste 105\, Severn\, MD 21144<br><br>**We will be c
 onducting a potluck and this is your opportunity to show off your culinary 
 skills and fancy imported beer. Please help us by updating our Google Doc w
 ith the food and drinks you’re bringing. <a href="https://tinyurl.com/y6c6p
 cy7">https://tinyurl.com/y6c6pcy7</a><br><br>**We look forward to seeing yo
 u there!<br><br>**Please RSVP at <a href="https://www.meetup.com/Unallocate
 d-Space/" id="ow457" __is_owner="true">https://www.meetup.com/Unallocated-S
 pace/events/265301478/</a><br><br>===<br><br>Frequently Asked Questions:<br
 ><br>(Q) What is the scheduled activities? (A)<br>– 3PM – 4PM – Smash Broth
 ers Tournament (and Mario Kart too)<br>– 4PM – Music\, Raffle\, Games<br>– 
 5PM – Food &amp\; Drinks<br>– 6PM – Board Announcements<br>– 6PM – Fire Tor
 nado (Round 1)<br>– 7PM – Raffle Winner Announcements<br>– 7PM – Fire Torna
 do (Round 2)<br>– 8PM-12AM – Camp-Style Fire<br><br>(Q) Who is invited? (A)
  Everyone! Twitter: “RT @Unallocated Space (of Severn\, MD) is having its 9
  Year Anniversary Party #hackerspace on Sat\, Nov 2nd\, 2019. Please join u
 s and RSVP!<br><br>(Q) Who is UAS? (A) Unallocated Space is a 501(c)(3) Non
 -profit Hackerspace. Our mission is to foster creative and technical growth
  through open collaboration by providing tools and resources within the gre
 ater Baltimore-Washington Metro area. Learn more at <a href="http://www.una
 llocatedspace.org">http://www.unallocatedspace.org</a> .<br><br>(Q) How to 
 support UAS? (A) Unlike most hackerspaces\, all of our events\, classes\, a
 nd workshops are completely open to the general public for free. We have co
 ntinued to serve the community in this manner for nine years. You can find 
 more about donating and volunteering at <a href="http://www.unallocatedspac
 e.org">http://www.unallocatedspace.org</a> .
LAST-MODIFIED:20191012T231430Z
LOCATION:Unallocated Space\, 512 Shaw Ct #105\, Severn\, MD 21144\, USA
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Unallocated Space 9th Anniversary Party
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
