DESCRIPTION:The morning of December 6th\, 2019 @ 12pm\, we close signups an
 d Elfster will choose who you should get a gift to (this is the most import
 ant part\; this is about the giving!). \n\nOnce you come back here to pick 
 up your match's information\, you'll have until December 14th\, 2019 to the
 n exchange our gifts at Unallocated Space. There is also (tentatively) an E
 pic Lan Party scheduled. Be prepared to be at Unallocated Space for the exc
 hange. \n\nYou do not have to stay after the exchange\, but seeing the gife
  received is what makes a Secret Santa fun! Try to stay within the spending
  limit\, and make sure you make a Wish List to give your person some good i
 deas. This is going to be lots of fun!\n\nSign Up Deadline\nFriday\, Decemb
 er 6\, 2019\n\nGift Exchange Date\nFriday\, December 14\, 2019\n\nRSVP At: 
 https://www.elfster.com/exchange/view/39741778/odnm/\n\nPlease RSVP and let
  me know if you're participating.\n\nWondering what a gift exchange is? It'
 s an event where everyone participating is randomly assigned to one another
 \, and each person anonymously gives and receives a gift.\n\nHope you'll jo
 in in the fun\,\nBuddy
