 nDATE: 5DEC2019\nTIME: 1900-2100\nTOPIC: INFOSEC NIGHT: Introduction to Web
  App Pen Testing Part 1 - Burp and Zap\nSUMMARY:This presentation will be a
 n introduction to web app pen testing\; specifically how to use Burp and Za
 p. These programs are commonly used during web penetration assessments\, we
 b app testing\, and can even be used in mobile app testing. We will go over
  some basics of web site functions\, cover basic functionality of the tools
 \, and provide some practice websites to tinker with. This is the first par
 t of a two part presentation series about web application pen testing.GOAL:
  Provide an introductory understanding of web application testingTHINGS TO 
 BRING: Note taking material\, laptop with Burp and/or Zap installed (or a K
 ali Linux distro)SKILL LEVEL: Everyone. Basic understanding of web technolo
 gies is helpful but will be covered during the presentationPRESENTER: nyte 
  
