 ceived a 3D printer learn to use it.&nbsp\;</p><p></p><p>THINGS TO BRING: Y
 ou may bring your 3D printer. Assembled or in parts. We also recommend a la
 ptop if you need software help.&nbsp\;</p><p></p><p>SKILL LEVEL: Beginner</
 p><p></p><p>PRESENTER: John/GreyBeard3D&nbsp\;</p><p></p><p>Come on out. In
  the first 45 minutes we will cover making/getting models\, Slicer software
  for preparing your prints\, and printing. The remaining time will be to pr
 ovide help\, assembly\, and troubleshooting.&nbsp\; We will wrap up at 3PM.
  An Extra hour is available for real challenging printers.&nbsp\;</p><p></p
 ><p>All ages welcome. Feel free to come if you just want to learn more abou
 t printers before buying one.&nbsp\;</p>
