  a few spare controllers I can lend for the event. Nintendo Switch Joycons\
 , Nintendo Switch Pro Controllers\, and Gamecube Controllers are all accept
 ed.&nbsp\;</p><p>Bringing your own Nintendo switch setup\, complete with a 
 Nintendo switch dock and a copy of Super Smash Bros. Ultimate for the Ninte
 ndo switch is appreciated\, but is only optional.</p><p>SKILL LEVEL:</p><p>
 This tournament is slightly geared toward players who want to start / have 
 only recently started playing competitively.</p><p>PRESENTER:</p><p>Chris D
 ove (<a href="http://twitch.tv/octochris">twitch.tv/octochris</a>)<br><br>K
 EYHOLDER:<br><br>Buddy</p>
