UID:3s5qeblaci0pca9qstik9qolcf@google.com
CREATED:20200108T005105Z
DESCRIPTION:<p>EDIT: Raspberry Jam will be postponed until April\, more inf
 o coming soon in Slack #raspi</p><p>https://www.unallocatedspace.org/2020/0
 3/13/covid-19-response-and-temporary-shutdown/<br><br>Unallocated Space is 
 hosting its second Raspberry Jam on March 14\, 2020 from 10am to 3pm</p><p>
 <strong>What is a Raspberry Jam?</strong></p><p>A birthday celebration to c
 elebrate everything we can do with a $35 computer. The day shall be filled 
 with events where anyone can show off projects they’ve made and learn new t
 hings by building projects with our instructors.</p><p><strong>Schedule:</s
 trong></p><p>10am-11am – Welcoming/Greeting<br><br>11am – First presentatio
 n – Introduction to Jam Day\, Raspberry Pi’s<br><br>12pm Workshops: tbd<br>
 <br>1pm Talks: tbd<br><br>2pm Show and Tell – For those who don’t want to t
 ake a scheduled block of time to show off new or previously built projects\
 , we’ll do firetalks here and now.<br></p><p><strong>Potential Projects:</s
 trong></p><ul><li><a href="https://projects.raspberrypi.org/en/projects/bui
 ld-a-robot">Build a Robot</a></li><li><a href="https://projects.raspberrypi
 .org/en/projects/whoopi-cushion">Whoopi Cushion</a></li><li><a href="https:
 //projects.raspberrypi.org/en/projects/turtle-race">Programming a Turtle Ra
 ce</a></li><li><a href="https://github.com/ccrisan/motioneyeos/wiki">Home S
 ecurity System</a></li><li><a href="https://retropie.org.uk/">How to build 
 a RetroPi</a></li><li>And more!</li></ul><p>All of our events are free\, bu
 t keeping the lights on is not. We’d like to suggest a $5 donation for this
  event\, but it is not required.</p><p>If you’d like to learn about support
 ing the space by becoming a member\,&nbsp\;<a href="https://www.unallocated
 space.org/membership">we’ve got a page just for you</a>!</p>
LAST-MODIFIED:20200313T190741Z
SEQUENCE:1
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Postponed- Jelly's Raspberry Jam Party 2020
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
