CREATED:20200926T150118Z
DESCRIPTION:Description:<br>Have you ever wanted to learn how to solder? Jo
 in us over Zoom on October 22nd at 6pm! We will walk you through the basics
  of safe soldering. You will be assembling the SparkFun WeevilEye kit. The 
 WeevilEye kit and a soldering kit are required for participation. You may a
 lready have some soldering supplies at home! A list of all recommended hard
 ware is listed below. We won't be including any supplies for this event\, y
 ou'll need to purchase supplies before the event\, the kit and a low cost s
 et of supplies are listed below. If you do not wish to purchase supplies bu
 t want to join the Zoom session\, feel free to drop in!<br><br>Zoom will be
  a new technology for us to teach a hands-on class. We will be utilizing ov
 erhead camera's to give you a close up view of our instructor in action. We
  will have breakout rooms when people need 1:1 support with an instructor.<
 br><br>For our next iteration of this class in November\, we will be buildi
 ng the following kit if you wish to save on shipping cost by buying both no
 w:&nbsp\;<a href="https://www.sparkfun.com/products/10212">https://www.spar
 kfun.com/products/10212</a><br><br>SparkFun WeevilEye:&nbsp\;<a href="https
 ://www.sparkfun.com/products/10723">https://www.sparkfun.com/products/10723
 </a><br><br>Cost friendly kit:&nbsp\;<a href="https://smile.amazon.com/Sold
 ering-Kit-Temperature-Desoldering-Electronics/dp/B07XKZVG8Z/">https://smile
 .amazon.com/Soldering-Kit-Temperature-Desoldering-Electronics/dp/B07XKZVG8Z
 /</a><br><br>Recommended kit: $13.95 -&nbsp\;<a href="https://smile.amazon.
 com/Soldering-Kit-Temperature-Desoldering-Electronics/dp/B07GTGGLXN/">https
 ://smile.amazon.com/Soldering-Kit-Temperature-Desoldering-Electronics/dp/B0
 7GTGGLXN/</a><br><br>Recommended materials:<br>- Soldering Iron<br>- Sponge
 <br>- Solder<br>- Solder sucker<br>- Wick<br>- Soldering Iron Holder<br>- H
 elping hands<br><br>Instructors: DigiReign\, Jelly\, Justin\, tbd<br><br>Zo
 om Link: https://zoom.us/j/96357417738<br><br>NOTE: Please email jelly@unal
 locatedspace.org or check slack for the Zoom passcode!
LAST-MODIFIED:20200926T150135Z
