DESCRIPTION:Description:<br>Have you ever wanted to learn how to solder? Jo
 in us over Zoom on November 19th at 6pm! We will walk you through the basic
 s of safe soldering. You will be assembling the SparkFun Electronic Dice ki
 t. The Electronic Dice kit and a soldering kit are required for participati
 on. You may already have some soldering supplies at home! A list of all rec
 ommended hardware is listed below. We won't be including any supplies for t
 his event\, you'll need to purchase supplies before the event\, the kit and
  a low cost set of supplies are listed below. If you do not wish to purchas
 e supplies but want to join the Zoom session\, feel free to drop in!<br><br
 >Zoom will be a new technology for us to teach a hands-on class. We will be
  utilizing overhead camera's to give you a close up view of our instructor 
 in action. We will have breakout rooms when people need 1:1 support with an
  instructor.<br><br>Decembers build is TBD.<br><br>We will be recording thi
 s event when the class has started and will warn everyone before recording 
 begins. We plan to upload the instructor view of the recording to YouTube/S
 ocial Media.<br><br>SparkFun Electronic Dice Kit:&nbsp\;<a href="https://ww
 w.sparkfun.com/products/10212">https://www.sparkfun.com/products/10212</a><
 br><br>Cost friendly kit:&nbsp\;<a href="https://smile.amazon.com/Soldering
 -Kit-Temperature-Desoldering-Electronics/dp/B07XKZVG8Z/">https://smile.amaz
 on.com/Soldering-Kit-Temperature-Desoldering-Electronics/dp/B07XKZVG8Z/</a>
 <br><br>Recommended kit: $13.95 -&nbsp\;<a href="https://smile.amazon.com/S
 oldering-Kit-Temperature-Desoldering-Electronics/dp/B07GTGGLXN/">https://sm
 ile.amazon.com/Soldering-Kit-Temperature-Desoldering-Electronics/dp/B07GTGG
 LXN/</a><br><br>Recommended materials:<br>- Soldering Iron<br>- Sponge<br>-
  Solder<br>- Solder sucker<br>- Wick<br>- Soldering Iron Holder<br>- Helpin
 g hands<br><br>Instructors: DigiReign\, Jelly\, Justin\, tbd<br><br>NOTE: P
 lease DM us for the Zoom passcode or check Slack!
