DESCRIPTION:\nUnfortunately due to unforeseen events our Presenter for the 
 Digital Forensics 102 class won't be able to make it in tonight...\n\nHowev
 er we were able to bring in BobbyR to Present "Cryptographic Components of 
 TLS/SSL"!\n\nPlease stop in at 7:00PM and find a seat tonight at Unallocate
