DESCRIPTION:\nWe will cover the basics of the Tor anonymity network includi
 ng operation\, use cases\, strengths\, weaknesses\, and what onions have to
  do with it.\n\nGOAL: Understand what Tor is\, how it works\, and how it ca
 n be a useful tool in your privacy toolbox.\n\nSKILL LEVEL: Everyone\nPRESE
 NTER: BobbyR
