 InfoSec Night - : Get Started on Hack the Box: Pen-testing Labs</strong></p
 ><p>SUMMARY: Discover the benefit of the free hack the box<br>platform to e
 nhanced your cyber security learning. HTB is an online platform to<br>test 
 and advance your skills in pen-testing and cyber security.</p><p>&nbsp\;</p
 ><p>GOAL: In this presentation\, you’ll gain insights into how to<br>get se
 tup to tackle the machines in the hack the box labs. My experience doing HT
 B for 15 days straight for fun. The difference<br>between the free HTB vs P
 aid HTB.</p><p>We’ll go cover the technique and concept to get an invite.<b
 r>(Chrome Developer tools\, Base64\, js \, etc). At the end of the presenta
 tion I’ll<br>provide assistance to the HTB invitation challenge.</p><p>&nbs
 p\;</p><p>THINGS TO BRING: A laptop w/ Kali if you want assistance with<br>
 going thru the invitation hack.</p><p>&nbsp\;</p><p>SKILL LEVEL: 0</p><p>&n
 bsp\;</p><p>PRESENTER: Samnang Som&nbsp\;</p>
