CREATED:20201101T172339Z
DESCRIPTION:Description:<br><br>*** This is a duplicate of our October even
 t for recording. People are still welcome and encouraged to join if you hav
 en't tried this already!!!<br>Have you ever wanted to learn how to solder? 
 Join us over Zoom on October 22nd at 6pm! We will walk you through the basi
 cs of safe soldering. You will be assembling the SparkFun WeevilEye kit. Th
 e WeevilEye kit and a soldering kit are required for participation. You may
  already have some soldering supplies at home! A list of all recommended ha
 rdware is listed below. We won't be including any supplies for this event\,
  you'll need to purchase supplies before the event\, the kit and a low cost
  set of supplies are listed below. If you do not wish to purchase supplies 
 but want to join the Zoom session\, feel free to drop in!<br><br>Zoom will 
 be a new technology for us to teach a hands-on class. We will be utilizing 
 overhead camera's to give you a close up view of our instructor in action. 
 We will have breakout rooms when people need 1:1 support with an instructor
 .<br><br>For our next iteration of this class in November\, we will be buil
 ding the following kit if you wish to save on shipping cost by buying both 
 now:&nbsp\;<a href="https://www.sparkfun.com/products/10212">https://www.sp
 arkfun.com/products/10212</a><br><br>SparkFun WeevilEye:&nbsp\;<a href="htt
 ps://www.sparkfun.com/products/10723">https://www.sparkfun.com/products/107
 23</a><br><br>Cost friendly kit:&nbsp\;<a href="https://smile.amazon.com/So
 ldering-Kit-Temperature-Desoldering-Electronics/dp/B07XKZVG8Z/">https://smi
 le.amazon.com/Soldering-Kit-Temperature-Desoldering-Electronics/dp/B07XKZVG
 8Z/</a><br><br>Recommended kit: $13.95 -&nbsp\;<a href="https://smile.amazo
 n.com/Soldering-Kit-Temperature-Desoldering-Electronics/dp/B07GTGGLXN/">htt
 ps://smile.amazon.com/Soldering-Kit-Temperature-Desoldering-Electronics/dp/
 B07GTGGLXN/</a><br><br>Recommended materials:<br>- Soldering Iron<br>- Spon
 ge<br>- Solder<br>- Solder sucker<br>- Wick<br>- Soldering Iron Holder<br>-
  Helping hands<br><br>Instructors: DigiReign\, Jelly\, Justin\, tbd<br><br>
 Zoom Link: <a href="https://zoom.us/j/96357417738">https://zoom.us/j/963574
 17738</a><br><br>NOTE: Please email <a href="mailto:jelly@unallocatedspace.
 org">jelly@unallocatedspace.org</a> or check slack for the Zoom passcode!
LAST-MODIFIED:20201101T172418Z
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Beginner Soldering Class
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
