DESCRIPTION:Description:<br>Have you ever wanted to learn how to solder? Jo
 in us over Zoom on January 21st at 6pm! We will walk you through the basics
  of safe soldering. You will be assembling a Tone Generator! The Tone Gener
 ator kit and a soldering kit are required for active participation but anyo
 ne is welcome to hang out in Zoom with us. If you have the Tesla Coil from 
 last month\, you'll be able to test the tone generator and coil connected t
 ogether!<br><br>Tesla Coil Kit:&nbsp\;&nbsp\;<a href="https://smile.amazon.
 com/gp/product/B01HM70CMY/">https://smile.amazon.com/gp/product/B01HM70CMY/
 </a><br><br>You may already have some soldering supplies at home! A list of
  all recommended hardware is listed below. We won't be including any suppli
 es for this event\, you'll need to purchase supplies before the event\, the
  kit and a low cost set of supplies are listed below. If you do not wish to
  purchase supplies but want to join the Zoom session\, feel free to drop in
 !<br><br>In February we will be building the Adventure Kit: 30 Days Lost in
  Space: https://inventr.io/product/adventure-kit-30-days-lost-in-space/<br>
 <br>Cost friendly soldering tools kit:&nbsp\;<a href="https://smile.amazon.
 com/Soldering-Kit-Temperature-Desoldering-Electronics/dp/B07XKZVG8Z/">https
 ://smile.amazon.com/Soldering-Kit-Temperature-Desoldering-Electronics/dp/B0
 7XKZVG8Z/</a><br><br>Recommended kit: $13.95 -&nbsp\;<a href="https://smile
 .amazon.com/Soldering-Kit-Temperature-Desoldering-Electronics/dp/B07GTGGLXN
 /">https://smile.amazon.com/Soldering-Kit-Temperature-Desoldering-Electroni
 cs/dp/B07GTGGLXN/</a><br><br>Recommended materials:<br>- Soldering Iron<br>
 - Sponge<br>- Solder<br>- Solder sucker<br>- Wick<br>- Soldering Iron Holde
 r<br>- Helping hands<br>- Grounding Strap<br><br>Instructors: DigiReign and
  Jelly
LAST-MODIFIED:20201208T005751Z
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Intermediate Soldering Event
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
