DESCRIPTION:<p>SUMMARY: Maryland Area Combat Robotics (MACRO) is hosting a 
 Test and Tune and open house.</p><p></p><p>GOAL: This event is being run to
  allow people to test their bots in an arena prior to the upcoming June 5 e
 vent\, and allow the public to see what we do\, ask questions and get to kn
 ow the MACRO staff.</p><p></p><p>THINGS TO BRING: 3d printed combat robots 
 for testing.&nbsp\; Please read the rules for construction&nbsp\;<a href="h
 ttp://macrobot.us/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/MACRO_Robot_Construction_Speci
 fications_v2021-03-25.pdf">http://macrobot.<wbr>us/wp-content/uploads/2021/
 04/<wbr>MACRO_Robot_Construction_<wbr>Specifications_v2021-03-25.pdf</a></p
 ><p></p><p>SKILL LEVEL: Novice to Expert.&nbsp\; If you know nothing and wa
 nt to know more\, this is a good event to learn.&nbsp\; If you know it all\
 , and want to help teach\, this is an excellent event.</p><p></p><p>PRESENT
 ER: Maryland Area Combat Robotics (MACRO</p><p>If you have questions\, we h
 ave an active Discord Server.&nbsp\;<a href="https://discord.gg/SXwArmv">ht
 tps://discord.gg/<wbr>SXwArmv</a></p>
