DESCRIPTION:Unallocated Space (UAS) Community Tech Swap Meet/Garage Sale (A
 nne Arundel\, MD)\n\nWe’d like to invite you\, your family\, and friends to
  our community tech swap meet/garage sale this Sunday\, July 18th\, 2021\, 
 7 am-3 pm\, rain or shine. The purpose of the sale is to clear space\, rais
 e money for future projects\, and encourage the community to recycle.\n\nSe
 e our Meetup announcement at https://www.meetup.com/Unallocated-Space/event
 s/[TBD] !\n\nLOCATION\n\nUnallocated Space\n512 Shaw Court\, Suite 105\nSev
 ern\, Maryland 21144\n\nWHAT WILL YOU FIND?\n\nAnything is possible. Things
  to expect to see for sale will vary\, but here are a few examples of what 
 to expect.\n\nmisc. servers and computers equipment * misc. antiquated hard
 ware * ethernet switches * ham radios * capacitors * audio equipment * peri
 pherals * cameras * WiFi equipment * lights * lasers * extension cords!! * 
 keyboards and mice * mystery boxes! * old and new TVs * high voltage power 
 supplies * tools * electrical equipment * etc.\n\nSELL YOUR STUFF!\n\nFor t
 hose considering setting up a table or taking space at this community event
 \, we are not requiring\, but recommending a $10 donation and welcome any o
 ther donations (cash or items). We will have tables for you to use\, but sp
 ace will be limited (first come\, first serve)\, but you are welcome to bri
 ng your own table.\n\nIf you’re interested in table space\, please contact 
 info (at) unallocatedspace (dot) org with the subject line “SWAP MEET SETUP
 ”.
LAST-MODIFIED:20210705T174727Z
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:UAS Community Tech Swap Meet/Garage Sale (Anne Arundel\, MD)
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
