DESCRIPTION:<html-blob><u></u><br><b>Memorial Day Weekend LAN Party</b></ht
 ml-blob><br><html-blob>Bring your gaming computer/laptop\, Switch and relat
 ed gaming peripherals. If you wanna pitch in for Pizza bring a few bucks\, 
 or your smart phone with PayPal password. — This event is being hosted from
  Unallocated Space and inviting all gamers to join us!<br><p><b>Event Plan:
 </b><br>Setup 12 Noon – 2PM<br>Gaming starts from 2PM and runs till Midnigh
 t.<br>Will aim to do dinner around 7PM<br>Tournament game will run around d
 inner time– Prize includes a gift card to be used with Gamestop/Amazon/Stea
 m Not to exceed 10$</p><p><b>Normal games we play:</b><br>L4D2 [usually as 
 an opener] [9.99]<br>Team Fortress 2 [ Free to play]<br>Among Us [4.99]<br>
 Unreal Tournament 2004 [ 14.99]</p><p><b>Some games on the table:</b><br>De
 ad By Daylight [19.99]<br>RUST [39.99]<br>Brawlhalla [free]<br>Phasmophobia
  [13.99]<br>7 Days to Die [24.99]<br>Sea of Thieves [19.99]<br>Paladins [ F
 ree to Play]<br>Keep Talking and Nobody Explodes [VR] [14.99 if you wanna g
 et your own copy]<br>Crab Game [Free]<br>Deceit [Free]<br>Darwin Project [F
 ree]<br>Fall Guys: Ultimate Knockout [ 19.99]<br>Killing Floor 2 [9.99]<br>
 Kukoro [Would require a stream]<br><br><br><br>Key holder: Nonie<br><br><br
 >RSVP:&nbsp\;<a href="https://www.meetup.com/Unallocated-Space/events/28614
 3415/">https://www.meetup.com/Unallocated-Space/events/286143415/</a></p><p
 ><br></p><u></u></html-blob>
