DESCRIPTION:Unallocated Space (UAS) Community Tech Swap Meet/Garage Sale (A
 nne Arundel\, MD)\n\nWe’d like to invite you\, your family\, and friends to
  our community tech swap meet/garage sale this Saturday\, July 16th\, 2022\
 , 7 am-3 pm\, rain or shine. The purpose of the sale is to clear space\, ra
 ise money for future projects\, and encourage the community to recycle.\n\n
 See our Meetup announcement at https://www.meetup.com/Unallocated-Space/eve
 nts/[TBD] !\n\nLOCATION\n\nUnallocated Space\n512 Shaw Court\, Suite 105\nS
 evern\, Maryland 21144\n\nWHAT WILL YOU FIND?\n\nAnything is possible. Thin
 gs to expect to see for sale will vary\, but here are a few examples of wha
 t to expect.\n\nmisc. servers and computers equipment * misc. antiquated ha
 rdware * ethernet switches * ham radios * capacitors * audio equipment * pe
 ripherals * cameras * WiFi equipment * lights * lasers * extension cords!! 
 * keyboards and mice * mystery boxes! * old and new TVs * high voltage powe
 r supplies * tools * electrical equipment * etc.\n\nSELL YOUR STUFF!\n\nFor
  those considering setting up a table or taking space at this community eve
 nt\, we are not requiring\, but recommending a $10 donation and welcome any
  other donations (cash or items). We will have tables for you to use\, but 
 space will be limited (first come\, first serve)\, but you are welcome to b
 ring your own table.\n\nIf you’re interested in table space\, please contac
 t info (at) unallocatedspace (dot) org with the subject line “SWAP MEET SET
 UP”.
LAST-MODIFIED:20220705T160205Z
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:UAS Community Tech Swap Meet/Garage Sale (Anne Arundel\, MD)
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
