  little history on light saber prop making and ordering parts for the build
 . \n\n\nSkills required: \nThese skills may or may not be needed depending 
 on choices make during the design phase. \nSoldering \nWire management \nDr
 illing and taping a hole. \nPainting\nCost: $60 to $350 average being $130
