DESCRIPTION:<pre><pre>Unallocated Space presents "Introduction to Ham Radio
 ". With the recent news regarding the FaceBook we want to talk with you abo
 ut alternate modes of communication. Imagine a decentralized form of commun
 ication where you don't need a cell phone tower or wifi\, that mode of comm
 unication is radios. Come join us with our presenter 5ocks\, KC3JKM\, will 
 talk with you about why to join the tradecraft\, how to get certified (easy
 )\, and what you need to get started (not much!). See you there\, 73.</pre>
 <a>https://zoom.us/j/98968859343?pwd=Tm9ETkMzcC9Ebi9sdHR2azRoSlhwQT09</a></
 pre>
