 y meetup. Everyone is welcome to attend this virtual event!<br><br>Our goal
  this meeting is to power through an RTL-SDR tutorial on decoding weather s
 atellite images in real time using NOAA or LEO satellites. Grab your RTL-SD
 R\, a laptop\, and let's decode some data together!!! <br><br>Instructions:
  https://www.rtl-sdr.com/rtl-sdr-tutorial-decoding-meteor-m2-weather-satell
 ite-images-in-real-time-with-an-rtl-sdr/<br><br><a href="https://zoom.us/j/
 98968859343?pwd=Tm9ETkMzcC9Ebi9sdHR2azRoSlhwQT09" id="ow653" __is_owner="tr
 ue">https://zoom.us/j/98968859343</a>
