DESCRIPTION:<html-blob><p>You’re invited to the Unallocated Space’s 12th An
 niversary Party!</p><p>The time is upon us again. It’s time to celebrate ou
 r successes with all our friends and patrons! Unallocated Space (UAS) cordi
 ally invites everyone to join us on Saturday\, November 12th\, 2022 to cele
 brate 12 years of providing the community a place to teach\, learn\, and bu
 ild. We haven’t celebrated since 2019\, so let’s make this a big one!</p><p
 >Unallocated has been going strong for 12 years\, and even survived a pande
 mic. Come out to eat\, drink\, and celebrate! As usual\, we plan on putting
  together the fire tornado.</p><p>Date/Time: Saturday\, November 12th\, 202
 2 / 4PM–12AM</p><p>Location: Unallocated Space\, 512 Shaw Ct Ste 105\, Seve
 rn\, MD 21144</p><p>We will be conducting a potluck and this is your opport
 unity to show off your culinary skills and fancy imported beer.&nbsp\;</p><
 p><b>Please help us by informing us about the food and drinks you’re bringi
 ng. <a href="https://www.perfectpotluck.com/RWVC1243"><u>https://www.Perfec
 tPotluck.com/RWVC1243</u></a></b></p><p>We look forward to seeing you there
 !</p><p>Please RSVP at <a href="https://www.meetup.com/unallocated-space/ev
 ents/289494379?utm_medium=referral&utm_campaign=share-btn_savedevents_share
 _modal&utm_source=link"><u>https://www.meetup.com/unallocated-space/events/
 289494379?utm_medium=referral&amp\;utm_campaign=share-btn_savedevents_share
 _modal&amp\;utm_source=link</u></a></p><p>&nbsp\;</p></html-blob>\n\nJoin w
 ith Google Meet: https://meet.google.com/hze-odoy-zfa\n\nLearn more about M
 eet at: https://support.google.com/a/users/answer/9282720
LAST-MODIFIED:20221102T125253Z
LOCATION:Unallocated Space\, 512 Shaw Ct Suite 105\, Severn\, MD 21144\, US
 A
