 printed plastic ant weight (1 pound) robot combat event\n\nGOAL: To increas
 e participation in robotic combat sports\, by lowering the financial barrie
 r to entry. To help participants learn engineering\, material science\, 3d 
 modeling\, 3d printing\, remote control systems and good sportsmanship\, wh
 ich all contribute to the enjoyment of robotic combat sports.\n\nTHINGS TO 
 BRING: One or more 3d printed combat robots\, which adhere to the construct
 ion rules laid out at here . There are a limited number of slots available\
 , so please register at robotcombatevents.com\n\nSKILL LEVEL: Beginner to E
 xpert.  We welcome all participants!\n\nPRESENTER: Maryland Area Combat Rob
 otics (MACRO)\n\nLive Stream: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCK5J7oVaIkWk
 hP8eDAGOxrA\n\nKeyholder: Ty McNeer/Jasen Stengel
