DESCRIPTION:<p><b>You’re invited to the Unallocated Space’s 13th Anniversar
 y Party!</b></p><p> </p><p><span>The moment we’ve all been waiting for is f
 inally here. It’s time to celebrate our successes with friends and patrons!
  Unallocated Space (UAS) warmly invites everyone to join us on Saturday\, D
 ec 9th\, 2023\, as we celebrate 13 years of offering the community a place 
 to teach\, learn\, and build.</span></p><p><span>We’re excited to update yo
 u on our recent achievements and express our gratitude to the outstanding i
 ndividuals who have contributed to our space this year. </span></p><p><span
 ><br></span><span>Expect ample food\, drinks\, guests\, and music. What wou
 ld a UAS party be without a fire tornado? Thankfully\, you don’t need to po
 nder that for too long. An epic fire tornado and campfire are on the agenda
 .</span></p><p> </p><p><span>** If you like having fun and meeting people w
 ith similar interests\, then this event is for you!</span></p><p><span>Date
 /Time: Saturday\, Dec 9th\, 2023 / 2PM–12AM</span></p><p><span>Location: Un
 allocated Space\, 512 Shaw Ct Suite #105\, Severn\, Maryland 21144</span><s
 pan><br></span></p><p><span>** Please RSVP at <a href="https://www.meetup.c
 om/unallocated-space/events/297285961">https://www.meetup.com/unallocated-s
 pace/events/297285961</a></span><span><br></span></p><p><span>** We’re host
 ing a potluck! Please help us by updating our perfect potluck with the food
  and drinks you’re bringing. Showcase your culinary skills and bring your b
 est dishes or imported beverages. Kindly update our potluck with the items 
 you’re bringing at </span><a href="https://www.perfectpotluck.com/meals.php
 ?t=TTGX8897"><span>https://www.perfectpotluck.com/meals.php?t=TTGX8897</spa
 n></a><span> .</span><span><br></span></p><p><span>**We can’t wait to see y
 ou!</span></p>
