DESCRIPTION:Epic LAN Party (Details subject to change)\nBring your gaming r
 ig\, (laptop/desktop)\, your **UPDATED** games/clients/OS\, Nintendo Switch
  and/or any related gaming peripherals. If you want to join in on pizza\, b
 ring a few bucks to pitch in on that\, or your smart phone with PayPal.\n\n
 Event Plan:\nSetup 1PM – 2PM\nGaming starts from 2PM and runs till Midnight
 \nWill aim to do dinner (pizza) around 7PM\nTournament "hot seat" game will
  run around dinner time\n\n\nGames we are most likely to play:\nL4D2 [usual
 ly as an opener] \nAmong Us \nUnreal Tournament 2004 \nGolf with friends\nB
 rawlhalla\nJackbox games\n\nOther likely options:\nDeep Rock Galactic\nKeep
  Talking and Nobody Explodes\nDungeon Defenders\nSea of Thieves\nPico Park\
 n\nSome other games on the table:\nDead By Daylight \nTeam Fortress 2\n7 Da
 ys to Die\nPaladins \nCrab Game\nDeceit\nDarwin Project\nFall Guys: Ultimat
 e Knockout\nKilling Floor 2\n\n\nA Note About Unallocated Space:\nWhile all
  events at Unallocated Space are free to all\, we do ask that you consider 
 making a donation to help us keep putting on events like this and others. Y
 our support is what keeps the lights on!!\n\n\nKey holders: Nonie\, Usako\,
  JT
LAST-MODIFIED:20231224T000146Z
LOCATION:512 Shaw Ct\, Severn\, MD 21144\, USA
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Epic LAN Party
TRANSP:OPAQUE
