DESCRIPTION:<span><br><p>Maryland Area Combat Robotics (MACRO) presents...<
 /p><h1><strong>Raging March Madness</strong></h1><p>Have you watched Battle
 Bots on TV?  Have you ever wanted to experience combat robotics\, up close\
 , personal and live? Well this is your chance!  MACRO will be hosting a com
 bat robotics event.  Come by and watch.  This event is open to the public a
 nd free to watch.  Donations to Unallocated Space are encouraged.</p><p>Mat
 ches will start at 11am.  Due to how tournament brackets work\, the highest
  density of matches per hour occur near the beginning of the event.</p></sp
 an>
