DESCRIPTION:<p>Charm City LUG is an officially recognized LEGO Users Group 
 (RLUG) offering a community for Adult Fans of LEGO (AFOL) based in Baltimor
 e\, Maryland and its surrounding region. Through displays across the state 
 and fan conventions nationwide\, our primary goal is to foster the enjoymen
 t of the LEGO brand as a toy\, a social tool\, and an art medium. </p><p>Du
 ring these meetings\, we discuss recent set reviews and LEGO news\, sort pa
 rts\, and present projects that members are working on. In addition\, we us
 e these meetings to discuss and plan for upcoming public events and shows a
 ll around the region and nation in which the LUG is represented by member b
 uilders showing off their work.</p><p>To learn more about Charm City LUG or
  to join\, check out our website: <a href="https://www.charmcitylug.com/" t
 arget="_blank">https://www.<wbr />charmcitylug.com/</a> <br></p>
