LOCATION:512 Shaw Ct Suite 105\, Severn\, MD 21144\, USA
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Charm City LUG August Aux Meeting
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
