DESCRIPTION:<p>You're invited to join us for our community Tech Swap Meet/G
 arage Sale/Moving Sale on Saturday\, September 21st\, 2024\, from 7 am to 3
  pm—rain or shine! This event aims to lighten the load for a pending move\,
  raise funds for future projects\, and promote recycling within our communi
 ty.</p><p></p><p></p><p>**LOCATION:**  </p><p>Unallocated Space  </p><p>512
  Shaw Court\, Suite 105  </p><p>Severn\, Maryland 21144</p><p></p><p></p><p
 >**WHAT CAN YOU EXPECT?**  </p><p>You never know what you’ll find! Items fo
 r sale will vary\, but here’s a glimpse of what may be available:</p><p></p
 ><p></p><p>- Miscellaneous servers and computer equipment  </p><p>- Vintage
  hardware  </p><p>- Ethernet switches  </p><p>- Ham radios  </p><p>- Capaci
 tors  </p><p>- Audio equipment  </p><p>- Peripherals  </p><p>- Cameras  </p
 ><p>- WiFi equipment  </p><p>- Lights and lasers  </p><p>- Extension cords 
  </p><p>- Keyboards and mice  </p><p>- Mystery boxes!  </p><p>- Monitors</p
 ><p>- Tools and electrical gear  </p><p>- And much more!</p><p></p><p>**WAN
 T TO SELL YOUR STUFF?**  </p><p>If you’d like to set up a table or reserve 
 space\, we suggest a $10 donation\, though it's not required. Additional ca
 sh donations are always welcome but unsold or unwanted items will not be ac
 cepted as we are purging to move. </p><p></p><p>We will provide tables\, bu
 t space is limited and on a first-come\, first-served basis. Feel free to b
 ring your own table if you prefer.</p><p></p><p>To reserve your space\, ple
 ase email us at board (at) unallocatedspace (dot) org with the subject line
  “SWAP MEET SETUP.”</p>
