LOCATION:512 Shaw Ct\, Suite 105\, Severn\, MD 21144\, USA
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:UAS Community Tech Swap Meet/ Garage Sale
TRANSP:OPAQUE
