 t Fans of <span>LEGO</span>®) members from Baltimore\, Maryland and its sur
 rounding area. We are spread across a wide range of ages\, backgrounds\, an
 d professions\, but all share the same love of <span>LEGO</span>. Some of o
 ur members have over 30 years of building experience with <span>LEGO</span>
 \, while others have newly discovered the hobby. Similarly some members enj
 oy the collecting aspect of the hobby or building official sets\, while oth
 ers focus their energy on building original creations\, commonly referred t
 o a MOC (My Own Creation). All of these interests are welcome\, and encoura
 ged. Our diversity is our strength and contributes to the wealth of knowled
 ge and experiences that we share among our membership. We welcome all <span
 >LEGO</span> enthusiasts\, from all backgrounds\, to participate in our eve
 nts and activities. Similarly we invite those within community who are 18 a
 nd older to consider joining us as a formal member of the LUG.</p><p>During
