DTSTART:20250204T230000Z
DTEND:20250205T030000Z
DTSTAMP:20250626T025311Z
UID:61bkgskukm0vsgnif54ugk64j9@google.com
CREATED:20250103T031007Z
DESCRIPTION:<br><br><p><strong>Queers and Beers (and Other Delightful Drink
 s!)</strong></p><p>Calling all people of the rainbow! Want to learn more ab
 out our hacker/maker space while meeting new people? Come to the inaugural 
 Queers and Beers (and Other Delicious Drinks) meetup!</p><p></p><p>This mee
 tup is open to all queer/LGBTQIA2S+ people whether you've been to Unallocat
 ed before or not.</p><p>At this is the first meeting\, let's talk about wha
 t we want to get from a meetup like this. The tone will be casual: come as 
 you are and be prepared to socialize. Bring drinks and snacks for yourself 
 or to share.</p><p><strong>Starting topic of conversation:</strong> <em>Who
  is your favorite queer coded villain?</em> Thea will be on hand with some 
 facts about the history of queer coding in American cinema. </p><p><strong>
 <br>THINGS TO BRING:</strong> Yourself\, some snacks\, and a tasty beverage
  (please be responsible and 21+ if you plan to bring alcohol)</p><p><strong
 ><br>PRESENTER: </strong>Thea</p>
LAST-MODIFIED:20250103T031007Z
LOCATION:1029 Benfield Blvd\, Millersville\, MD 21108\, USA
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Queers and Beers (and Other Delightful Drinks!)
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
