CREATED:20250118T002852Z
DESCRIPTION:<p><strong>Machine Sewing 101 Lesson 1: Sewing and Fabric Basic
 s</strong></p><p></p><p dir="ltr"><span>New to machine sewing? Used to sew 
 but forgot how? This class is for you! </span></p><p></p><p dir="ltr"><span
 >Machine Sewing 101 is a six-lesson course for beginners. We will start wit
 h the basics of sewing machine use and fabric selection and build on our sk
 ills as we progress. Each lesson will have a hands-on activity.</span></p><
 p></p><p dir="ltr"><span>Lesson 1: Sewing &amp\; Fabric Basics</span></p><p
  dir="ltr"><span>Lesson 2: Quilting 1: Bowl Cozy</span></p><p dir="ltr"><sp
 an>Lesson 3: Quilting 2: Pot Holder/Hot Pad</span></p><p dir="ltr"><span>Le
 sson 4: Zippers and Pockets and Tote Bags\, Oh My!</span></p><p dir="ltr"><
 span>Lesson 5: Apparel Sewing: Using a Pattern</span></p><p dir="ltr"><span
 >Lesson 6: Apparel Sewing: Drafting a Pattern</span></p><p></p><p dir="ltr"
 ><span>Lesson 1 covers:</span></p><ul><li dir="ltr"><p dir="ltr"><span>A ve
 ry brief history of sewing</span></p></li><li dir="ltr"><p dir="ltr"><span>
 Mechanics and parts</span></p></li><li dir="ltr"><p dir="ltr"><span>Presser
  feet</span></p></li><li dir="ltr"><p dir="ltr"><span>Stitches</span></p></
 li><li dir="ltr"><p dir="ltr"><span>Fabric talk</span></p></li><li dir="ltr
 "><p dir="ltr"><span>Cutting woven fabric</span></p></li><li dir="ltr"><p d
 ir="ltr"><span>Sewing woven fabric</span></p></li><li dir="ltr"><p dir="ltr
 "><span>Activity: Petal Drawstring Bag</span></p></li></ul><p dir="ltr"><sp
 an><b>THINGS TO BRING:</b></span></p><ul><li dir="ltr"><p dir="ltr"><span>S
 ewing machine</span></p></li><li dir="ltr"><p dir="ltr"><span>Two fat quart
 ers or two 12”x12” squares of fabric</span></p></li><li dir="ltr"><p dir="l
 tr"><span>String or ribbon</span></p></li><li dir="ltr"><p dir="ltr"><span>
 Coordinating thread</span></p></li><li dir="ltr"><p dir="ltr"><span>Iron</s
 pan></p></li><li dir="ltr"><p dir="ltr"><span>Scissors</span></p></li><li d
 ir="ltr"><p dir="ltr"><span>Straight pins</span></p></li><li dir="ltr"><p d
 ir="ltr"><span>Ruler</span></p></li></ul><p></p><p dir="ltr"><span>We have 
 limited supplies for this class. If you would like to use our supplies\, pl
 ease consider making a small donation to Unallocated Space.</span></p><p></
 p><p dir="ltr"><span>Don’t have a sewing machine? Unallocated does! We have
  two machines for use during class. Please email </span><a href="mailto:eve
 nts@unallocatedspace.org" target="_blank"><span><u>events@unallocatedspace.
 org</u></span></a><span> and let us know if you need to use one. Reservatio
 ns for a sewing machine will be accepted on a first come\, first served bas
 is.</span></p><p></p><p dir="ltr"><span><b>SKILL LEVEL:</b></span><span> Be
 ginner</span></p><p><span><b>PRESENTER:</b></span><span> Thea</span></p>
LAST-MODIFIED:20250118T002852Z
LOCATION:1029 Benfield Blvd\, Millersville\, MD 21108\, USA
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Machine Sewing 101 Lesson 1: Sewing and Fabric Basics
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
