 n 2 if you have a basic understanding of how a sewing machine works.</span>
 </p><p></p><p dir="ltr"><span><b>THINGS TO BRING:</b></span></p><ul><li dir
 ="ltr"><p dir="ltr"><span>Sewing machine</span></p></li><li dir="ltr"><p di
 r="ltr"><span>Two fat quarters or two 10” squares of cotton fabric</span></
 p></li><li dir="ltr"><p dir="ltr"><span>Two 9” squares of cotton batting</s
 pan></p></li><li dir="ltr"><p dir="ltr"><span>Matching thread</span></p></l
 i><li dir="ltr"><p dir="ltr"><span>Scissors</span></p></li><li dir="ltr"><p
