 pan>Iron</span></p></li><li dir="ltr"><p dir="ltr"><span>Ruler or measuring
  tape</span></p></li></ul><p></p><p dir="ltr"><span>We have a limited suppl
 ies for this class. If you would like to use our supplies\, please consider
  making a small donation to Unallocated Space.</span></p><p></p><p dir="ltr
 "><span>Don’t have a sewing machine? Unallocated does! We have two machines
  you can use during the class. Please email </span><a href="mailto:events@u
 nallocatedspace.org" target="_blank"><span><u>events@unallocatedspace.org</
 u></span></a><span> and let us know if you need to use one. Reservations fo
 r a sewing machine will be accepted on a first come\, first served basis.</
 span></p><p></p><p dir="ltr"><span><b>SKILL LEVEL:</b></span><span> Beginne
 r</span></p><p></p><p dir="ltr"><span><b>PRESENTER:</b></span><span> Thea</
