DESCRIPTION:<p><strong>Machine Sewing 101 Lesson 3: Quilting 2</strong></p>
 <p></p><p dir="ltr"><span>New to machine sewing? Used to sew but forgot how
 ? Then this class is for you! </span></p><p></p><p dir="ltr"><span>Machine 
 Sewing 101 is a six-lesson course for beginners. We will start with the bas
 ics of sewing machine use and fabric selection and build on our skills as w
 e progress. Each lesson will have a hands-on activity.</span></p><p></p><p 
 dir="ltr"><span>Lesson 1: Sewing &amp\; Fabric Basics</span></p><p dir="ltr
 "><span>Lesson 2: Quilting 1: Bowl Cozy</span></p><p dir="ltr"><span>Lesson
  3: Quilting 2: Pot Holder/Hot Pad</span></p><p dir="ltr"><span>Lesson 4: Z
 ippers and Pockets and Tote Bags\, Oh My!</span></p><p dir="ltr"><span>Less
 on 5: Apparel Sewing: Using a Pattern</span></p><p dir="ltr"><span>Lesson 6
