 ace.org" target="_blank"><span><u>events@unallocatedspace.org</u></span></a
 ><span> and let us know if you need to use one. Reservations for a sewing m
 achine will be accepted on a first come\, first served basis.</span></p><p>
 </p><p dir="ltr"><span><b>SKILL LEVEL:</b></span><span> Beginner</span></p>
