UID:0fpovqqtmsks8ueqjoeisqugpe@google.com
CREATED:20250130T013156Z
DESCRIPTION:<p><strong>Charm City LUG Feb Aux Meeting</strong></p><p>Due to
  Charm City Lego User Group's bylaws\, you must be over 18 to attend or joi
 n.</p><p></p><p>Charm City LUG is made up of over 50 AFOL (Adult Fans of LE
 GO®) members from Baltimore\, Maryland and its surrounding area. We are spr
 ead across a wide range of ages\, backgrounds\, and professions\, but all s
 hare the same love of LEGO. Some of our members have over 30 years of build
 ing experience with LEGO\, while others have newly discovered the hobby. Si
 milarly some members enjoy the collecting aspect of the hobby or building o
 fficial sets\, while others focus their energy on building original creatio
 ns\, commonly referred to a MOC (My Own Creation). All of these interests a
 re welcome\, and encouraged. Our diversity is our strength and contributes 
 to the wealth of knowledge and experiences that we share among our membersh
 ip. We welcome all LEGO enthusiasts\, from all backgrounds\, to participate
  in our events and activities. Similarly we invite those within community w
 ho are 18 and older to consider joining us as a formal member of the LUG.</
 p><p></p><p>During these meetings\, we hold themed build challenges\, discu
 ss recent set reviews and LEGO news\, and hold presentations from members h
 ighlighting interesting build techniques and projects they are working on. 
 In addition\, we use these meetings to discuss and plan for upcoming public
  events and shows all around the region and nation in which the LUG is repr
 esented by member builders showing off their work.</p><p></p><p>Outside of 
 monthly meetings\, members meet for sorting parties\, collaborative build p
 rojects\, public and private build events\, and general socialization. </p>
 <p></p><p>You can check out our upcoming meetings and events on the Charm C
 ity LUG website.</p><p></p><p><a href="https://www.charmcitylug.com/" targe
 t="_blank">https://www.charmcitylug.com/</a></p>
LAST-MODIFIED:20250208T035534Z
LOCATION:1029 Benfield Blvd\, Millersville\, MD 21108\, USA
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Charm City LegoUG Feb Aux Meeting
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
