CREATED:20250208T035618Z
DESCRIPTION:<span><div dir="auto">LEGO Day<div dir="auto"><div dir="auto">A
 ll LEGO enthusiast\, their families and children (ages 4 &amp\; up) are wel
 come to join Unallocated Space for a fun filled evening of building and dis
 covery! This fun event includes some of the following activities:<div dir="
 auto"><div dir="auto">– Building with LEGOs!<div dir="auto">– Discover with
  LEGOs!<div dir="auto">– Swapping LEGOs!</span><div dir="auto">– Drinks &am
 p\; Snacks @ 4 PM<span><div dir="auto">– Show Off Your Designs<div dir="aut
 o">– Discuss LEGO Events / Communities<div dir="auto">– Donate LEGOs to Una
 llocated Space (for Future Events)<div dir="auto"></span><div dir="auto">Pl
 ease help us track interest in our events by RSVPing on Meetup<div dir="aut
 o"><div dir="auto">Date &amp\; Time: Sunday\, March 2nd\, 2025 from 3-5 PM<
 div dir="auto"><div dir="auto">Location:<div dir="auto">Unallocated Space<d
 iv dir="auto">1029 Benfield Blvd. <div dir="auto">Millersville\, MD 21108
