DESCRIPTION:*CANCELED*\nUnfortunately we are experiencing a power issue and
  this is also affecting the heat so we will not be hosting tonight's open h
 ouse! 😢 \n\nOpen House Night - Come join us and check out what UAS is all 
 about. Keyholders and members will be available to answer questions\, help 
 with projects\, and give tours. If you've never been to UAS before\, this i
 s a great time to check us out. We host a weekly open house to help introdu
 ce new people to the space and some of the various interests and participan
 ts. Come on by\, and check out the space and some of the fun projects we ar
 e working on.\n\nHosting Keyholder: Whitney
