BEGIN:VEVENT
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20220511T180000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20220511T220000
DTSTAMP:20250626T025311Z
UID:6hgmccph68s36b9h60p30b9k6orjibb2c8p68bb4c8ojad32cdh3ep9nc8@google.com
RECURRENCE-ID;TZID=America/New_York:20220511T180000
CREATED:20211113T184050Z
DESCRIPTION:Open House Night - Come join us and check out what UAS is all a
 bout. Keyholders and members will be available to answer questions\, help w
 ith projects\, and give tours. If you've never been to UAS before\, this is
  a great time to check us out. We host a weekly open house to help introduc
 e new people to the space and some of the various interests and participant
 s. Come on by\, and check out the space and some of the fun projects we are
  working on.\n\nHosting Keyholder: Whitney\n\nLock Sport Meet Up- Purpose \
 nCurrently our meetup exists to support a hands on approach for beginners w
 ho want to learn about pin and tumbler lock-picking. Veteran pickers who wa
 nt to discuss more advanced topics like security pins\, different locking m
 echanisms\, key impressioning\, decoding\, and safe manipulation are all we
 lcome\, but there is an Advanced lockpicking night as well.\n\nFormat \nTyp
 ically we cover a primer on the single pin picking (SPP) of pin and tumbler
  locks over the course of 15 minutes. Then spend about 35-40 doing hands on
  picking together before moving back to class-wide Q&A briefly. Then we spe
 nd the rest of the time picking and sharing advice. The 15 minutes of the p
 resentation is formal\, the rest is casual. \n\n\nEquipment \nIf you have l
 ockpicks or locks you’re encouraged to bring them. We do have a set of begi
 nner locks and picks anyone can use. \n\nHosting Keyholder: MacGnG
LAST-MODIFIED:20250212T195240Z
LOCATION:512 Shaw Ct\, Severn\, MD 21144\, USA
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Open House & Lock Sport
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
