DESCRIPTION:Queers and Beers (and Other Delightful Drinks!)\n\nCalling all 
 people of the rainbow! Want to learn more about our hacker/maker space whil
 e meeting new people? Come to Queers and Beers (and Other Delightful Drinks
 )!\n\nThis meetup is open to all queer/LGBTQIA2S+ people whether you've bee
 n to Unallocated before or not.\n\nThe tone will be casual: come as you are
  and be prepared to socialize. Bring drinks and snacks for yourself or to s
 hare. There will be some craft supplies if you want to make something.\n\nT
 HINGS TO BRING: Yourself\, some snacks\, and a tasty beverage (please be re
 sponsible and 21+ if you plan to bring alcohol)\n\nPRESENTER: Thea
