DESCRIPTION:SUMMARY:  The DEF CON Group 443\, also known as DC443\, is an i
 nterest group designed to discuss general hacking and its culture.  Feburar
 y 3rd wil be an introductory demo to virtualization & penetration testing u
 sing publicly-available vulnerable VM images. Press-a-button\,-do-a-thing a
 ims to:\n o Install VirtualBox\n o Import Kali Linux .ova\n o Import vulner
 able VM .ova\; pwn VM\n o Install WinXP from .iso\; make vuln\; pwn XP VM\n
  o export vuln WinXP .ova for friends/fun/profit\n \n Website: https://dc44
 3.org\n Twitter: https://twitter.com/dc443_\n \n GOAL: get comfy & pop shel
 ls\n \n THINGS TO BRING: a Laptop (Windows-centric but any will work)\n \n 
 SKILL LEVEL: Beginner (or stump-the-chump pros)\n \n Key: Adam (Digital Tin
 ker)\n Presenter: 5ocks
