CREATED:20250206T161101Z
DESCRIPTION:<b>Hosts</b>: Nonie &amp\; JT<br><b>Co-Hosts when they can atte
 nd</b>: Usako &amp\; DT<br><br><b>Times</b>: 1PM - Midnight!<br><b>Setup ti
 me</b>: From 1-2PM EST<br><br><b>Games likely to be played: <br></b>Left4De
 ad2<br>AmongUs<br>Marvel Rivals<br>Jackbox<br>R.E.P.O. <br>Darwin Project<b
 r>Party Animals<br>Deep Rock Galactic<br>Crab Game<br><br>Other games could
  come up during the event\, we ask you update your games PRE LAN party\, so
  if we do need to download something during the event it is quickly done.<b
 r><br>We find plugging into the Ethernet for the event does help the transf
 er speeds go much faster. While Wireless is available it is discouraged for
  the LAN event. Please make sure you can connect to the network physically 
 via Ethernet to USB\, or having a port extension available. <br><br>We will
  likely do a Pizza Order for food\, but all are encouraged to bring food fo
 r the event as well such as Sodas\, Snacks\, Paper towels\, paper plates\, 
 cups and so on. These supplies do get shared with other events and future L
 AN parties if made available. But we encourage to drop 5$ in the donation b
 ox to help pay for internet\, electricity\, or pizza orders. We provide thi
 s event for free for our community and being a Non-Profit organization\, ev
 ery dollar helps. :)
